quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf bohat bari shan walay iss quran ki qasam
  50,2,bulkay enhen tajjub maloom hua kay inn kay pass inhi mein say aik aagah kerney wala aaya to kafiron ney kaha kay yeh aik ajeeb cheez hai
  50,3,kiya jabb hum mar ker mitti hojayen gay phir yeh wapsi door (az aqal) hai
  50,4,Zamin jo kuch inn mein say ghatati hai who humen maloom hai aur humaray pass sabb yaad rakhnay waali kitab hai
  50,5,Buklay inhon nay sachi baat ko jhoot kaha hai jabkay who inn kay pass phonch chuki pus who aik uljhao mein par gaye hain
  50,6,Kiya inhon nay aasman ko apnay uper nahi dekha? Kay hum ney ussay kiss tarah banaya aur zeenat di hai iss mein koi shigaf nahi
  50,7,Aur zamin ko hum ney bicha diya hai aur iss mein hum ney pahaar daal diye hain aur iss mein hum ney qisam qisam ki khushnuma cheezen uga di hain
  50,8,Takay her rujoo kernay walay bandey kay liye beenaee aur daanaaee ka zariya ho
  50,9,Aur hum ney aasman say babarkat pani barsaya aur iss say baghaat aur katney walay khet k ghallay peda kiye
  50,10,Aur khujuron kay buland-o-bala darakht jinkay khoshay teh ba teh hain
  50,11,Bandon ki rozi kay liye aur hum ney pani say murda shehar ko zinda ker diya. Issi tarah (qabron say) nikalna hai
  50,12,Inn say pehlay Nooh ki qom ney aur rass walon ney aur samood ney
  50,13,Aur aad ney aur firaon ney aur biradran-e-loot ney
  50,14,Aur aeeka walon ney aur tubba ki qom ney bhi takzeeb ki thi.sab ney payghambron ko jhutlaya pus mera wada-e-azab inn per sadiq aagaya
  50,15,Kiya hum pehli baar kay peda kerney say thak gaye? Bulkay yeh log naee pedaeesh ki taraf say shak mein hain
  50,16,Hum ney insan ko peda kiya hai aur iss kay dil mein jo khayalat uthtay hain unn say hum waqif hain aur hum uss ki rag-e-jaan say bhi ziyadah uss say qareeb hain
  50,17,Jiss din do lenay walay ja letay hain aik dayen taraf aur aik bayen taraf betha hua hai
  50,18,(Insan) mun say koi lafz nikal nahi pata magar kay usskay pass nigheban tayyar hai
  50,19,Aur mot ki beyhoshi haq ley ker aa phonchi yehi hai jiss say tu bidakta phirta tha
  50,20,Aur soor phonk diya jayega.Wada-e-azab ka din yehi hai
  50,21,Aur her shaks iss tarah aayega kay uss kay sath aik lanay wala hoga aur aik gawahee denay wala
  50,22,Yaqeenan tu iss say ghaflat mein tha lekin hum ney teray samney say pardah hata diya pus aaj teri nigah bohat tez hai
  50,23,Uss ka humnasheen (farishta) kahega yeh hazir hai jo kay meray pass tha
  50,24,Daal do jahannum mein her kafir sirkash ko
  50,25,Jo nek kaam say rikney wala aur hadd say guzar janay wala aur shak kerney wala tha
  50,26,Jiss ney Allah k sath doosra mabood bana liye tha pus iss say sakht azab mein daal do
  50,27,Iss ka humnasheen (shetan) kahega aey humaray rab! Mein ney issay gumrah nahi kiya tha bulkay yeh khud hi door daraz ki gumrahi mein tha
  50,28,Haq taalaa farmaye ga bus meray samney jhagray ki baat mat kero mein to pehlay hi tumhari taraf waeed (wada-e-azab) bhej chuka tha
  50,29,Meray haan baat badalti nahi aur na hi mein apnay bandon per zara bhi zulm kerney wala hun
  50,30,Jiss din hum dozakh say poochen gay kiya tu bhar chuki? Woh jawab dey di kiya kuch aur ziyadah bhi hai
  50,31,Aur jannat perhezgaron kay liye bilkul qareeb kerdi jayegi zara bhi door na hogi
  50,32,Yeh hai jiss ka tum say wada kiya jata tha her uss shaks kay liye jo rujoo kerney wala aur pabandi kerney wala ho
  50,33,Jo rehman ka ghaeebana khof rakhta ho aur tawajja wala dil laya ho
  50,34,Tum iss jannat mein salamti kay sath dakhil hojao. Yeh hamesha rehney ka din hai
  50,35,Yeh wahan jo chahyen unhen milay ga (bulkay) humaray pass aur bhi ziyadah hai
  50,36,"Aur inn say pehlay bhi hum boht si ummaton ko halak ker chukay hain jo inn say taqat mein bohat ziyadah thi woh shehron mein dhondtay hi reh gaye, kay koi bhagney ka thikana hai"
  50,37,Iss mein her sahib-e-dil kay liye ibrat hai aur uss kay liye jo dil say mutawajja hoker kaan lagaye aur woh hazir ho
  50,38,Yaqeenan hum ney aasmanon aur zamin aur jo kuch iss kay darmiyan hai sab ko (sirf) cheh (6) din mein peda kerdiya aur humen thakaan ney chua tak nahi
  50,39,Pus yeh jo kuch kehtay hain aap iss per sabar keren aur apnay rab ki tasbeeh tareef kay sath biyan keren sooraj nikalney say pehlay bhi aur sooraj ghuroob honey say pehlay bhi
  50,40,Aur raat kay kissi waqt bhi tasbeeh keren aur namaz kay baad bhi
  50,41,Aur sunn rakhen kay jiss din aik pukarney wala qareeb hi ki jagah say pukaray ga
  50,42,"Jiss roz uss tund-o-tez cheekh ko yaqeen kay sath sunn len gay, yeh din hoga nikalney ka"
  50,43,Hum hi jilatay hain aur hum hi martay hain aur humari hi taraf lot phir ker aana hai
  50,44,Jiss din zamin phat jayegi aur yeh dortay huye (nikal paren gay) yeh jama kerlena hum per boht hi aasan hai
  50,45,Yeh jo kuch keh rahey hain hum bakhoobi jaantay hain aur aap inn per jabar kerney walay nahi to aap quran kay zariyey enhen samjhatay rahen jo meray waeed (daraway kay wadon) say dartay hain
  51,1,qasam hai bikherney waliyan ki ura ker
  51,2,Phir uthaney waliyan bojh ko
  51,3,Phir chalney waliyan narmi say
  51,4,Phir kaam ko taqseem kerney waliyan
  51,5,Yaqeen mano kay tum say jo wadey kiye jatay hain (sab) sachay hain
  51,6,Aur be-shak insaf honey walahai
  51,7,Qasam hai raahon walay aasman ki
  51,8,Yaqeenan tum mukhtalif baat mein paray huye ho
  51,9,Iss say wohi baaz rakha jatahai jo pher diya gaya ho
  51,10,Bey savad baten kerney walay gharat kerdiye gayr
  51,11,Jo ghaflat mein hain aur bhoolay huye hain
  51,12,Poochtey hain kay yom-e-jaza kab hoga
  51,13,han yeh woh din hai kay yeh aag per tapaye jayen gey
  51,14,Apni fitna-perdazi ka maza chakho yehi hai jiss ki tum jaldi macha rahey thay
  51,15,Be-shak taqwa walay log bahishton aur chashmon mein hongey
  51,16,unn kay rab ney jo kuch unhen ata farmaya hai ussay ley rahey hongey woh to iss say pehlay hi nekokaar thay
  51,17,Woh raat ko boht kum soya kertay thay
  51,18,Aur waqt-e-sahar istaghfaar kiya kertay thay
  51,19,Aur unkay maal mein mangney walon ka aur sawal say bachney walon ka haq tha
  51,20,Aur yaqeen walon kay liye to zamin mein boht si nishaniyan hain
  51,21,Aur khud tumhari zaat mein bhi to kiya tum dekhtay ho
  51,22,Aur tumhari rozi aur jo tum say wada kiya jata hai sab aasman mein hai
  51,23,Aasman-o-zamin kay perwerdigar ki qasam! kay yeh bilkul barhaq hai aisa hi jaisay kay tum baten kertay ho
  51,24,Kiya tujhay ibrahim(alh-e-salam)kay moazziz mehmanon ki khabar bhi phonchi hai
  51,25,Woh jab unkay han aaye to salam kiya ibrahim ney jawab-e-salam diya(aur kaha yeh to) ajnabi log hain
  51,26,Phir (Chup chaap jaldi jaldi) apney ghar walon ki taraf gaye aur aik farba bachrey (ka gosht) laye
  51,27,Aur issay unkay passrakha aur kaha aap khatay kiyon nahi
  51,28,phir to dil hi dil mein unn say khofzada hogaye. unhon ney kaha aap khof na kijiye aur unhon ney uss (hazrat Ibrahim) ko aik ilm walay larkay ki bisharat di
  51,29,Pus unki biwi aagay barhi aur heyrat mein aaker apney mun per hath maar ker kaha kay mein to burhiya hun aur sath hi banjh
  51,30,Unhon ney kaha han teray perwerdigar ney issi tarah farmaya hai. be-shakwoh hakeem-o-aleem hai
  51,31,(Hazrat Ibrahim alh-e-salam) ney kaha kay Allah kay bhejay huye (farishton!)tumhara kiya maqsad hai
  51,32,Unhon ney jawab diya kay hum gunagar qom ki taraf bhejay gaye hain
  51,33,Takay hum unn per kitti kay kankar barsayen
  51,34,Jo teray rab ki taraf say nishan zada hain unn had say guzar janay walon kay liye
  51,35,Pus jitney eman walay wahan thay hum ney unhen nikal liya
  51,36,Aur hum ney wahan musalmanon ka sirf aik hi ghar paya
  51,37,Aur wahan hum ney unkay liye jo dardnaak azab ka darr rakhtey hain aik(kamil) alamat chori
  51,38,Musa(alh-e-salam kay qissay) mein (bhi humari taraf say tanbeeh hai) kay hum ney ussay firaon ki taraf khuli daleel dey ker bheja
  51,39,Pus uss ney apney balbootay per mun mora aur kehney laga yeh jadoogar hai ya deewana hai
  51,40,Bil-aakhir hum ney ussay aur uss kay lashkaron ko apney azab mein pakar ker darya mein daal diya woh tha hi malamat kay qabil
  51,41,Iss tarah aadiyon mein bhi (humari taraf say tanbeeh hai) jabkay hum ney unn say khali aandhi bheji
  51,42,Woh jiss jiss cheez per girti thi ussay boseedah hadi ki tarah (choora choora) kerdeti thi
  51,43,Aur samood (kay qissay) mein bhi (ibrat) hai jab unsay kaha gaya kay tum kuch dino tak faeedah uthalo
  51,44,Lekin unhon ney apney rab kay hukum say sirtabi ki jiss per unhen unkay dekhtay dekhtay (tez-o-tund) karakay ney halak kerdiya
  51,45,Pus na woh kharay hosakay aur na badla ley sakay
  51,46,Aur Nooh(alh-e-salam) ki qom ka bhi iss say pehlay (yehi haal ho chuka tha) woh bhi baray nafarman log thay
  51,47,Aasman ko hum ney (apney) hathon say banaya hai aur yaqeenan hum kushadgi kernay walay hain
  51,48,Aur zamin ko hum ney farsh banadiya hai pus hum boht hi achay bichanay walay hain
  51,49,Aur her cheez ko hum ney jora jora peda kiya hai takay tum naseehat hasil kero
  51,50,Pus tum Allah ki taraf dor bhag (yani rujoo) kero yaqeenan main tumhen uss ki taraf say saaf saaf tanbeeh kernay wala hun
  51,51,Aur Allah kay sath kissi aur ko mabood na therao. be-shak mein tumhen uss ki taraf say khula daraney wala hun
  51,52,Issi tarah jo log inn say pehlay guzray hain unkay pass jo bhi rasool aaya unhon ney keh diya ya to yeh jadoogar hai ya deewana hai
  51,53,Kiya yeh iss baat ki aik doosray ko wassiyat kertay gaye hain
  51,54,(Nahi) bulkay yeh sab kay sab sirkash hain to app inn say mun pher len. aap per koi malamat nahi
  51,55,Aur naseehat kertay rahen yaqeenan yeh naseehat eman walon ko nafa degi
  51,56,Mein ney jinnat aur insanon ko mehaz issi liye peda kiya hai kay woh sirf meri ibadat keren
  51,57,Na mein inn say rozi chchta hun na meri yeh chahat hai kay yeh mujhay khilayen
  51,58,Allah taalaa to khud hi sab ka rozi rasan tawanaee wala aur zor awar hai
  51,59,Pus jin logon ney zulm kiya hai unhen bhi unkay sathiyon kay hissay kay nuisil hissa mileyga lehaza woh mujh say jaldi talab na keren
  51,60,Pus kharabi hai munkiron ko unkay uss din ki jiss ka wada diye jatay hain
  52,1,Qasam hai toor ki
  52,2,Aur likhi hui kitab ki
  52,3,Jo jhilli kay khulay huye warq mein hai
  52,4,Aur abad ghar ki
  52,5,Aur unchi chat ki
  52,6,Aur bharkaye huye samandar ki
  52,7,Be-shak app kay rab ka azab hoker rehnay wala hai
  52,8,Ussay koi rokney wala nahi
  52,9,Jiss din aasman thar tharaney lagay ga
  52,10,Aur pahaar chalney phirney lagen gey
  52,11,uss din jhutlaney walon ki (poori) kharabi hai
  52,12,Jo apni behuda goee mein uchal kood ker rahey hain
  52,13,Jiss din woh dhakkay dey ker aatish jahannam ki taraf laye jayen gey
  52,14,Yehi wohi aatish dozakh hai jissay tum jhoot batlatey thay
  52,15,(Abb batao) kiya yeh jadoo hai? ya tum dekhtay hi nahi ho
  52,16,Jao dozakh mein abb tumhara sabar kerna aur na kerna tumharay liye yaksan hai tumhein faqat tumharay kiye ka badla diya jayega
  52,17,Yaqeenan perhezgar log jannaton mein aur nematon mein hain
  52,18,Jo unhen unkay rab ney dey rakhi hain uss per khush khush hain aur unkay perwerdigar ney unhen jahannam kay azab say bhi bacha liya hai
  52,19,Tum mazay say khatay peetay raho inn aemaal kay badlay jo tum kertay thay
  52,20,Baraber bichay huye shandar takhtay per takkiye lagaye huye aur hum ney unkay nikkah bari bari aankhon wali(hooron) say kerdiye hain
  52,21,Aur jo log eman laye aur unki olad ney bhi eman mein unki perwi ki hum unki olad ko unntak phoncha dengey aur unkay amal say hum kuch kum na keren gey.her shaks apney aemaal ka girwi hai
  52,22,Hum unkay liye meway aur marghoob gosht ki rail pail kerden gey
  52,23,(khush tabaee kay sath) aik doosray say jam (sharab) ki cheena jhapta keren gey jiss sharab kay suroor mein to beyhuda goee hogi na gunah
  52,24,Aur unkay gird unkay no-umer ghulam chal phir rahey hongey goya kay woh moti thay ji dhakay rakhay thay
  52,25,Aur aapas mein aik doosray ki taraf mutawajja hoker sawal kerengey
  52,26,kahen gey iss say pehlay hum apney ghar walon kay dar miyan boht dara kertay thay
  52,27,Pus Allah taalaa ney hum per bara ehsan kiya aur humen tez-o-tund garum hawaon kay azab say bacha liya
  52,28,Hum iss say pehlay hi uss ki ibadat kiya kertay thay be-shak woh mohsin aur meharban hai
  52,29,To aap samjhatay rahen kiyoh kay app apney rab kay fazal say na to kaahin hain na deewana
  52,30,Kiya kafir yun kehtay hain kay yeh shaeer hai hum iss per zamaney kay hawadis (yani mot) ka intezar ker rahey hain
  52,31,Keh dijiye! tum muntazir raho mein bhi tumharay sath intezar kernay walon mein hun
  52,32,Kiya inki aqlen enhen yehi sikhati hain? ya yeh log hi sirkash hain
  52,33,Kiya yeh kehtay hain kay iss nabi ney khud qharh liya hai waqya yeh hai kay woh eman nahi latey
  52,34,Acha agar yeh sachay hain to bhala iss jaisi aik (hi) baat yeh (bhi) to ley aayen
  52,35,Kiya yeh baghair kissi(peda kernay walay) kay khud ba khud peda hogaye hain? ya yeh khud peda kernay walay hain
  52,36,Kiya inhon ney hi aasman aur zamin ko peda kiya hai? bulkay yeh yaqeen na kernay walay log hain
  52,37,ya kiya inkay pass teray rab kay khazaney hain?ya (in khazanon kay) yeh darogha hain
  52,38,Ya kiya inkay pass koi seerhi hai jiss per charh ker suntay hain?(agar aisa hai) to inka sunnay wala koi roshan daleel pesh keray
  52,39,Kiya Allah ki to sab larkiyan hain aur tumharay han larkay hain
  52,40,Kiya tu inn say koi ujrat talab kerta hai kay yeh uskay tawaan say bojhal ho rahey hain
  52,41,Kiya inkay pass ilm-e-gheeib hai jissay yeh likh letay hain
  52,42,Kiya yeh log koi fareb kerna chahtay hain? to yaqeen kerlen kay fareeb khordah kafir hi hain
  52,43,Kiya Allah kay siwa inka koi mabood hai? (hergiz nahi) Allah taalaa inkay shirk say pak hai
  52,44,Agar yeh log aasman kay kissi tukray ko girta hua dekhlen tab bhi yeh keh den key yeh teh-ba-teh badal hai
  52,45,Tu enhen chor dey yahan tak kay enhen uss din say sabiqa paray jiss mein yeh beyhosh kerdiye jayen gey
  52,46,Jiss din enhen inka makar kuch kaam na dey ga aur na woh madad kiye jayen gey
  52,47,Be-shak zalimon kay liye iss kay ilawa aur azab bhi hain lekin inn logon mein say aksar bey-ilm hain
  52,48,Tu apney rab kay hukum kay intezar kein sabar say kaam ley be-shak tu humari aankhon kay samney hai subah ko jab tu uthay apney rab ki paki aur hamd biyan ker
  52,49,Aur raat ko bhi usski tasbeeh parh aur sitaron kay doobtay waqt bhi
  53,1,Qasam hai sitarey ki jab woh girey
  53,2,Kay tumharey sathi ney na raah gum ki hai na woh terhi raah per hai
  53,3,Aur na woh apni khuwaish say koi baat kehtay hain
  53,4,Woh to sirf wahi hai jo utari jaati hai
  53,5,Issay poori taqat walay farishtey ney sikhaya hai
  53,6,Jo zor -aawar hai phir woh seedha khara hogaya
  53,7,Aur woh buland aasmanon kay kinaron per tha
  53,8,Phir nazdeek hua aur utar aaya
  53,9,Pus woh do kamanon kay ba-qadar fasla reh gaya bulkay iss say bhi kum
  53,10,Pus uss ney ALLAH kay bandaey ko wahi phonchaee jo bhi phonchaee
  53,11,Dil ney jhoot nahi kaha jissay (payghumber ney) dekha
  53,12,Kiya tum jhagra kertay ho iss per jo (payghumber) dekhtey hain
  53,13,Issay to aik martaba aur bhi dekha tha
  53,14,Sidrat-ul-muntaha kay pass
  53,15,Issi kay pass jannat-ul-maawa hai
  53,16,Jabkay sidrah ko chupaye leti thi woh cheez jo uss per cha rahi thi
  53,17,Na to nigah behki na had say barhi
  53,18,Yaqeenan uss ney apney rab ki bari bari nishaniyon mein say baaz nishaniyan dekha len
  53,19,Kiya tum ney laat aur uzza ko dekha
  53,20,Aur manaat teesray pichlay ko
  53,21,Kiya tumharay liye larkay aur ALLAH kay liye larkiya hain
  53,22,Yeh to abb bari beyinsafi ki taqseem hai
  53,23,DAR-asal yeh sirf naam hain jo tum ney aur tumharay baap dadon ney inkay rakh liye hain Allah ney inki koi daleel nahi utaari yeh log to sirf atkal kay aur apni nafsaani khuwaishon kay peechay paray huye hain aur yaqeenan unkay rab ki taraf say unkay pass hidayat aa chuki hai
  53,24,Kiya her shaks jo aarzoo keray ussay mayassar hai
  53,25,Allah hi kay hath hai yeh hajaan aur woh jahaan
  53,26,Aur boht say farishtay aasmanon mein hain jinki sifarish kuch bhi nafa nahi dey sakti magar yeh aur baat hai kay Allah taalaa apni khushi aur apni chahat say jioss kay liye chahye ijazat dey dey
  53,27,Be-shak jo log aakhirat per eman nahi rakhtay woh farishton ka zanana naam muqarrar kertay hain
  53,28,Halankay unhen iss ka koi ilm nahi woh sirf apney gumaan kay peechay paray huye hain aur be-shak weham(o-guman) haq kay muqablay mein kuch kaam nahi deta
  53,29,To app iss say mun mor len jo humari yaad say mun moray aur jinka iradah ba-juz zindagan-e-duniya kay aur kuch na ho
  53,30,Yehi inn kay ilm ki inteha hai aap ka rab iss say khoob waqif hai jo iss ki raah say bhatak gaya hai aur wohi khoob waqif hai iss say bhi jo raah yafta hai
  53,31,Aur Allah hi ka hai jo kuch aasmanon mein hai. aur jo. kuch zamin mein hai takay Allah taalaa buray amal kerney walon ko unkay aemaal ka badla dey aur nek kaam kerney walon ko acha badla inayat farmaye
  53,32,Inn logon ko jo baray gunahon say bachtay hain aur beyhayaee say bhi siwaye kissi chotay say gunah kay be-shak tera rab boht kushada maghfirat wala hai woh tumhen bakhoobi jaanta hai jabkay uss ney tumhen zamin say peda kiya aur jabkay tum apni maaon kay pet mein bachay thay pus tum apni pakeezgi aap biyan na kero wohi pehezgaron ko khoob janta hai
  53,33,Kiya app ney ussay dekha jiss ney mun mor liya
  53,34,Aur boht kuin diya aur hath kio rok liya
  53,35,Kiya ussay ilm-e-ghaib hai kay woh (sab kuch) dekh raha hai
  53,36,Kiya ussay iss cheez ki khabar nahi di gaee jo musa (alh-e-salam) kay kay
  53,37,Aur wafadaar Ibrahim (alh-e-salam) kay saheefon mein tha
  53,38,Kay koi shaks kissi doosray ka bojh na uthayega
  53,39,Aur yeh kay her insan kay liye sirf wohi hai jiss ki kosish khud uss ney ki
  53,40,Aur yeh kay be-shak uss ki kosish unqareeb dekhi jayegi
  53,41,Phir ussay poora poora badla diya jayega
  53,42,Aur yeh kay aap kay rab hi ki taraf phonchna hai
  53,43,Aur yeh kay wohi hansata hai aur wohi rulata hai
  53,44,Aur yeh kay wohi maarta hai aur jilata hai
  53,45,Aur yeh kay ussi ney jora yani nar-o-mada peda kiya hai
  53,46,Nutfay say jabkay woh tapkaya jata hai
  53,47,Aur yeh kay ussi kay zimmey doobara peda kerna hai
  53,48,Aur yeh kay wohi maaldar banata hai aur sarmaya deta hai
  53,49,Aur yeh kay wohi sheyara (sitaray) ka rab hai
  53,50,Aur yeh kay ussi ney aad awwal ko halak kiya hai
  53,51,Aur samood ko bhi (jin men say) aik ko bhi baqi na rakha
  53,52,Aur iss say pehlay Qom-e-nooh ko yaqeenan woh baray zalim aur sirkash thay
  53,53,Aur motafiqa (shehar ya utti hui bastiyon ko) ussi ney ulat diya
  53,54,Phir uss per cha diya jo chaya
  53,55,Pus aey insan tu apney rab ki kiss neimat kay baray mein jhagray ga
  53,56,Yeh (nabi) daranay walay hain pehlay daramay walon mensay
  53,57,Aanay wali ghari qareeb aagaee hai
  53,58,Allah kay siwa iss ka (waqt moayyen per khol) dikhaney wala koi nahi
  53,59,Pus tum kiya iss baat say tajjub kertay ho
  53,60,Aur hans rahey ho? rotay nahi
  53,61,(Bulkay) tum khel rahey ho
  53,62,Abb Allah kay samney sajday kero aur (ussi ki) ibadat kero
  54,1,Qayamat qareeb agaee aur chand phat gaya
  54,2,Yeh agar koi mojzza dekhtay hain to mun pher letay hain aur kehdetay hain. kay yeh pehlay say chala aata hua jadoo hai
  54,3,inhon ney jhutlaya aur apni khuwaishon ki pairwi ki aur her kaam theray huye waqt per muqarrar hai
  54,4,yaqeenan inn kay pass woh khabren aa chuki hain jin mein dant dapat (ki naseehat) hai
  54,5,Aur kamil aqal ki baat hai lekin in darawni baaton ney bhi kuch faeedah na diya
  54,6,Pus (aey nabi) tum inn say aeyraaz kero jiss din aik pukarnay wala nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukaray ga
  54,7,yeh jhuki aankhon qabron say iss tarah nikal kharay hongay kay goya woh phela hua taddi dal hai
  54,8,Pukarnay walay ki taraf dortay hongay aur kafir kahengey yeh din to boht sakht hai
  54,9,Inn say pehlay qom-e-nooh ney bhi humaray banday ko jhulaya tha aur deewana batla ker jhirak diya gaya tha
  54,10,Pus uss ney apney rab say dua ki kay mein beybus hun tu meri madad ker
  54,11,Pus hum ney aasman kay darwazon ko zor kay menh say khol diya
  54,12,Aur zamin say chashmon ko jaari kerdiya pus uss kaam kay liye jo muqaddar kiya gaya tha (dono) paani jama hogaye
  54,13,Aur hum ney issay takhton aur keelon wali (kashti) per sawar kerliya
  54,14,Jo humari aankhon kay samnay chal rahi thi badla uss ki taraf say jiss ka kufur kiya gaya tha
  54,15,Aur be-shak hum ney iss waqaey ko nishani bana ker baqi rakha pus koi hai naseehat hasil kerney wala
  54,16,Batao mera azab aur meri daraney wali baaten kaisi rahen
  54,17,Aur be-shak hum ney quran ko samajhney kay liye aasan kerdiya hai pus kiya koi naseehat hasil kerney wala hai
  54,18,Qom-e-aad ney bhi jhutlaya pus kaisa hua mera azab aur meri daraney wali baten
  54,19,Hum ney unn per tez-o-tund musalsal chalney wali hawa aik peham manhoos din mein bhej di
  54,20,Jo logon ko utha utha ker dey patakhti thi goya kay woh jarr say katey huye khajoor kay taney hain
  54,21,Pus kaisi rahi meri saza aur mera darana
  54,22,Yaqeenan hum ney quran ko naseehat kay liye aasan kerdia hai pus kiya koi hai naseehat hasil kerney wala
  54,23,Qom-e-samood ney daraney walon ko jhutlaya
  54,24,Aur kehney lagay kiya humi mein say aik shaks ki hum farmanbardaari kerney lagen? tab to hum yaqeenan ghalati aur deewangi mein paray huye hongey
  54,25,Kiya humaray sab kay darmiyan sirf issi per wahi utaari gaee nahi bulkay woh jhoota shekhi khor hai
  54,26,Abb sab jaan lengey kal ko kay kon jhoota aur shekhi khor tha
  54,27,Be-shak hum unki aazmaeesh kay liye untni bhejen gey pus (aey saleh) tu inka muntazir reh aur sabar ker
  54,28,Han enhen khabar kerdey kay paani in mein taqseem shuda hai her aik apni baari per hazir hoga
  54,29,Unhon ney apney sathi ko awaz di jiss ney (untni per) waar kiya aur (uss ki) kochen kaat den
  54,30,Pus kiyon ker hua mera azab aur mera darana
  54,31,Hum ney unn per aik cheekh bheji pus aisay hogaye jaisay baar bananay walay ki rondhi hui ghaas
  54,32,Aur hum ney naseehat kay liye quran ko aasan kerdia hai pus kiya hai koi jo naseehat qabool keray
  54,33,Qom-e-Loot ney bhi daraney walon ki takzeeb ki
  54,34,Be-shak hum ney unn per pathar barsaney wali hawa bheji siwaye loot(alh-e-salam) kay ghar walon kay waqt nijat deydi
  54,35,Apney ehsan say her her shukarguzaar ko hum issi tarah badla detay hain
  54,36,Yaqeenan loot (alh-e-salam) ney unhen humari pakar say daraya tha lekinunhon ney daraney walon kay baray mein (shak-o-shuba aur) jhagra kiya
  54,37,Aur inn loot (alh-e-salam) ko unkay mehmanon kay baray mein phuslaya pus hum ney unki aankhen andhi kerden (aur kehdia) mera azab aur mera darana chakho
  54,38,Aur yaqeeni baat hai kay unhen subah saweray hi aik jagah pakarney walay muqarra azab ney ghaarat kerdia
  54,39,Pus meray azab aur meray darawey ka maza chakho
  54,40,Aur yaqeenan hum ney quran ko Pind-o-waaz kay liye aasan kerdia hai pus kiya koi hai naseehat pakarney wala
  54,41,Aur firaoniyon kay pass bhi daraney walay aaye
  54,42,Unhon ney humari tamamnishaniyan jhutlayen pus hum ney unhen baray ghalib qavi pakarney walay ki tarah pakar liya
  54,43,(Aey qureshiyo!) kiya tumharay kafir inn kafiron say kuch behtar hain? ya tumharay liye agli kitabon mein chutkara likha hua hai
  54,44,Ya yeh kehtay hain kay hum ghalba panay wali janat hain
  54,45,Unqareeb yeh jamat shikast di jayegi aur peeth deyker bhagey gi
  54,46,Bulkay qayamat ki ghari unkay waday kay waqt hai aur qayamat bari sakht aur kerwi cheez hai
  54,47,Be-shak gunehgaar gumrahi mein aur azab mein hain
  54,48,Jiss din woh apney mun kay bal aag mein ghaseetay jayen gey.(aur unn say kaha jayega) dozakh ki aag lagney kay mazay chakho
  54,49,Be-shak hum ney her cheez ko aik (muqarra) andazay per peda kia hai
  54,50,Aur humara hukum sirf aik dafa (ka aik kalma) hi hota hai jaisey aankh ka jhapakna
  54,51,Aur hum ney tum jaisey bohteron ko halak kerdia hai pus koi hai naseehat lenay wala
  54,52,Jo kuch enhon ney (aemaal) kiye hain sab naam-e-aemaal mein likhay huye hain
  54,53,(Issi tarah) her choti bari baat bhi likhi hui hai
  54,54,Yaqeenan humara darr rakhney walay jannaton aur neharon mein hongay
  54,55,Raasti aur izzat ki bethak mein qudrat walay badshah kay pass
  55,1,Rehman ney
  55,2,Quran sikhaya
  55,3,Ussi ney insan ko peda kiya
  55,4,Aur ussay bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Aftab aur mahtab (muqarra) hisab hain
  55,6,Aur sitaray aur darakht dono sajdah kertay hain
  55,7,Ussi ney aasman ko buland kiya aur ussi ney tarazoo rakhi
  55,8,Takay tum tolnay mein tajawuzz na kero
  55,9,Insaf kay sath wazan ko theek rakho aur tol mein kum na do
  55,10,Aur ussi ney makhlooq kay liye zameen bichadi
  55,11,Jiss mein meway hain aur khoshay walay khajoor kay darakht hain
  55,12,Aur bhuss wala anaj hai aur khushboodar phool hain
  55,13,Pus (aey insano aur jinno!) tum apney perwerdigaar ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,14,Uss ney insan ko bajney wali mitti say peda kiya jo theekri ki tarah thi
  55,15,Aur jinnaat ko aag kay sholay say peda kiya
  55,16,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,17,Woh rab hai dono mashriqon aur dono maghribon ka
  55,18,To(aey jinno aur insano) tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,19,Uss ney do darya jaari kerdiye jo aik doosray say nil jaatay hain
  55,20,Inn dono mein aik aar hai kay uss say barh nahi saktay
  55,21,Pus apney perwerdigaar ki kon kon si nemat ko jhutlao hey
  55,22,Inn dono mein say miti aur mongey baraamad hotay hain
  55,23,Phir tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,24,Aur Allah hi ki (milkiyat mein) hain woh jahaaz jo samandaron mein pahaar ki tarah buland (chal phir rahey) hain
  55,25,Pus (aey insano aur jinno!) tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,26,Zamin per jo hain sab fana honay walay hain
  55,27,Sirf teray rab ki zaat jo azmat aur izzat wali hai baqi reh jayegi
  55,28,Phir tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,29,Sab aasman-o-zamin walay ussi say maantay hain her roz woh aik shaan mein hai
  55,30,Phir tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,31,(Jinno aur insanon kay giroho!) unqareeb hum tumhari taraf poori tarah mutawajja hojayen gey
  55,32,Phir tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhut ao gey
  55,33,Aey giroh-e-jinnaat-o-insan! zamin kay kinaron say bahir nikal janay ki taqat hai to nikal bhago! baghair ghalba aur taqat kay tum nahi nikal saktay
  55,34,Phir apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,35,Tum per aag kay sholay aur dhuwan chora jayega phir tum muqabla na ker sako gey
  55,36,Phir apney rab ki nematon mein say kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,37,Pus jabkay aasman phat ker surkh hojaye jaisay kay surkh chamra
  55,38,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,39,Uss din kissi insan aur kissi jinn say uss kay gunahon ki pursish na ki jayegi
  55,40,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,41,Gunahgaar sirf huliye say hi pehchan liye jayen gey aur unki peshaniyon kay baal aur qadam pakar liye jayen gey
  55,42,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,43,Yeh hai woh jahannum jissay mujrim jhoota jaantay thay
  55,44,Uss kay aur kholtay huye garum paani kay darmiyan chakkar khayen gey
  55,45,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,46,Aur uss shaks kay liye jo apney rab kay samnay khara honay say dara do jannaten hain
  55,47,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,48,(Dono jannaten) boht si tehniyon aur shakhon wali hain
  55,49,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,50,Inn dono (jannaton) mein behtay huye chashmay hain
  55,51,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,52,Inn dono jannaton mein her qisam kay mewon ki do qismen hongi
  55,53,Phir tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,54,Jannati aisay farashon per takkiya lagaye huye hongay jinkay astar dabeez resham kay hongay aur inn dono jannaton kay meway bilkul qareeb hongay
  55,55,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlaogey
  55,56,Wahan (sharmeeli) neechi nigah wali hooren hain jinhen unn say pehlay kissi jinn-o-ins ney hath nahi lagaya
  55,57,Pus apney paalnay walay ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhtlao gey
  55,58,Woh hooren misil yaqoot aur mongay kay hongi
  55,59,Pus tum apney perwerdigaar ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,60,Ehsan ka badla ehsan kay siwa kiya hai
  55,61,Pus apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,62,Aur inn kay siwa do jannaten aur hain
  55,63,Pus tum apney perwerish kernay walay ki kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,64,Jo dono gehri sabz siyahi maeel hain
  55,65,Batao abb apney perwerdigaar ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhtlao gey
  55,66,Inn mein do(josh say) ubalnay walay chashmay hain
  55,67,Phir tum apney rab ki kon konsi nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,68,Inn dono mein meway aur khajoor aur anaar hongay
  55,69,Kiya abb bhi rab ki kissi nemat ki takzeeb tum kerogay
  55,70,Inn mein nek seerat khoobsurat orten hain
  55,71,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,72,(gori rangat ki) hooren jannati khemon mein rehnay waaliyah hain
  55,73,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,74,Unnko hath nahi lagaya kissi insan ya jinn ney iss say qabal
  55,75,Pus apney perwerdigaar ki kon konsi nemat ko jhtlao gey
  55,76,Sabz masnadon aur undah farshon per takkiya lagaye huye hongay
  55,77,Pus tum apney rab ki kiss kiss nemat ko jhutlao gey
  55,78,Teray perwerdigar ka naam ba barkat hai jo izzat-o-jalal wala hai
  56,1,Jab Qayamat qaeem hojaye gi
  56,2,Jiss kay waqaye honay mein koi jhoot nahi
  56,3,Woh pust kernay wali aur buland kernay wali hogi
  56,4,Jab kay zameen zalzala kay sath hila di jayegi
  56,5,Aur pahar bilkul reza reza kerdiye jayen gey
  56,6,phir woh misil paragandah ghubaar kay hojayen gey
  56,7,Aur tum teen jamaton mein hojaogey
  56,8,pus dahanay hath walay kaisay achay hain dahanay hath walay
  56,9,Aur bayen hath walay kiya haal hai bayen hath walon ka
  56,10,Aur jo aagey walay hain woh to aagay walay hi hain
  56,11,Woh bilkul nazdeeki haasil kiye hain
  56,12,Nematon wali jannaton mein hain
  56,13,(Boht bara) giroh to aglay logon mein say hoga
  56,14,Aur thoray say pechlay. logon mein say
  56,15,yeh log sonay kay taaron say banay huye takhton per
  56,16,aik doosray kay samnay takiya lagaye bethay hongay
  56,17,Inn kay pass aisay larkay jo humesha(larkay hi) rahen gey aamdoraft keren gey
  56,18,Aabkhoray aur jug ley ker aur aisa jaam ley ker jo behti hui sharab say pur ho
  56,19,jiss say na sir mein dard ho na aqal mein fatoor aaye
  56,20,Aur aisay meway liye huye jo inki pasand kay hon
  56,21,Aur parindon kay gosht joenhein marghoob hon
  56,22,Aur bari bari aankhon wali hoorien
  56,23,Jo chupay huye motiyon ki tarah hain
  56,24,Yeh sila hai unkay aemaal kal
  56,25,Na wahan bakwas sunein gey aur na gunnah ki baat
  56,26,Sirf salam hi salam ki awaz hogi
  56,27,Aur dahanay hath walay kiya hi achay hain dahanay hath walay
  56,28,Woh baghair kanton ki bairiyon
  56,29,Aur teh ba teh keelon
  56,30,Aur lambay lambay sayon
  56,31,Aur behtay huye paaniyon
  56,32,Aur ba-kasrat phalon main
  56,33,Jo na khatam hon na rok liye jayen
  56,34,Aur unchay unchay farshon mein hongay
  56,35,Hum ney unn(Ki biwiyon ko) khaas tor per banaya hai
  56,36,Aur hum ney unhen kanwariyan banadiya hai
  56,37,Mohabbat waliyan aur hum umar hain
  56,38,Dayen hath walon kay liye hain
  56,39,jamm-e-ghafeer aglon main say
  56,40,Aur boht bari jamat hai pichlon main say
  56,41,Aur bayen hath walay kiya hai bayen hath walay
  56,42,Garum hawa aur garum paani mein (hongey)
  56,43,Aur siyah dhuyen kay saye mein
  56,44,Jo na thanda hai na farhat buksh
  56,45,Be-shak yeh log iss say pehlay boht nazon mein palay huye thay
  56,46,Aur baray baray gunahon per israr kertay thay
  56,47,Aur kehtay thay kay kiya jab hum mar jayengey aur mithi aur haddi hojayengey to kiya hum phir doobara utha kharay kiye jayeugey
  56,48,Aur kiya humaray aglay baap dada bhi
  56,49,Aap keydijiye kay yaqeenan sab aglay aur pichlay
  56,50,zaroor jama kiye jayegey aik muqarra din kay waqt
  56,51,Phir tum aey gumraho jhutlanay walon
  56,52,Albatta khanay walay ho thoher ka darakht
  56,53,Aur ussi say pet bharnay walay ho
  56,54,Phir uss per garum kholta paani peenay walay ho
  56,55,Phir peenay walay bhi piyasay unton ki tarah
  56,56,Qayamat kay din unki mehmaain yeh hai
  56,57,Hum hi ney tum sab ko peda kiya hai phir tum bawer nahi kertay
  56,58,Acha phir yeh to batlao kay jo mani tum tapkatay ho
  56,59,kiya uss ka (insane) tum banatay ho ya peda kernay walay hum hi hain
  56,60,Hum hi ney tum mein mot ko mutaeyen kerdiya hai.aur iss say haray huye nahi hain
  56,61,Kay tumhari jagah tum jaisay aur peda kerden. aur tumhen naye siray say uss aalam mein peda keren jiss say tum (bilkul) beykhabar ho
  56,62,Tumhen yaqeeni tor per pehli dafa ki pedaaeesh maloom hi hai phir kiyon ibrat hasil nahi kertay
  56,63,Acha phir yeh bhi batlao kay tum jo kuch botay ho
  56,64,Ussay tum hi ugatay ho ya hum uganay walay hain
  56,65,Agar hum chahyen to ussay reza reza ker dalen aur tum heyrat kay sath baten banatay hi reh jao
  56,66,Kay hum per to tawaan hi par gaya
  56,67,Bulkay hum bilkul mehroom hi reh gaye
  56,68,Acha yeh batao kay jiss pani ko tum peetay ho
  56,69,Ussay baadlon say bhi tum hi utartay ho ya hum barsatay hain
  56,70,Agar humari mansha hoto hum issay kerwa zehar kerden phir tum humari shukar guzari kiyon nahi kertay
  56,71,Acha zara yeh bhi batao kay jo aag tum sulgatay ho
  56,72,Iss kay darakht ko tum ney peda kiya hai ya hum uss kay peda kernay walay hain
  56,73,Hum ney issay sabab-e-naseehat aur musafiron kay faeeday ki cheez banaya hai
  56,74,Pus apney boht baray rab kay naam ki tasbeeh kiya kero
  56,75,Pus mein qasam khata hun sitaron kay girnay ki
  56,76,Aur agar tumhen ilm hoto yeh boht bari qasam hai
  56,77,Kay be-shak yeh quran boht bari izzat wala hai
  56,78,Jo aik mehfooz kitab mein darj hai
  56,79,Jissay sirf pak log hi chu saktay hain
  56,80,Yeh rabul aalameen ki taraf say utra hua hai
  56,81,Pus kiya tum aisa baat ko sirsari (aur mamooli) samajh rahe ho
  56,82,Aur apney hissay mein yehi letay ho kay jhutlatey phiro
  56,83,Pus jabkay rooh narkharay tak phonch jaye
  56,84,Aur tum uss waqt aankhon say dekhtay raho
  56,85,Hum uss shaks say banisbat tumharay boht ziyadah qareeb hotay hain lekin tum nahi dekh saktey
  56,86,Pus agar tum kissi kay zair-e-farman nahi
  56,87,Aur iss qol mein sachay hoto (zara) iss rooh ko to lotao
  56,88,Pus jo koi barah-e-elaahi say qareeb kiya hua hoga
  56,89,Ussay to rahat hai aur ghizayen hain aur aaram wali jannat hai
  56,90,Aur jo shaks dahanay walon mein say hai
  56,91,To bhi salamti hai teray liye kay tu dahanay walon mein say hai
  56,92,Lekin agar koi jhut lanay walon gumrahaon mein say hai
  56,93,To kholtay huye garum pani ki mehmaani hai
  56,94,Aur dozakh mein jana hai
  56,95,Yeh khabar sirasir haq aur qaton yaqeeni hai
  56,96,Pus tu apney azeem-ul-shaan perwerdigar ki tasbeeh ker
  57,1,Aasmanon aur zamin mein jo hai (Sub) Allah ki tasbeeh ker rahey hain woh zabardast ba-hikmat hai
  57,2,Aasmanon aur zamin ki badshahat ussi ki hai.woh hi zindagi deta hai aur mot bhi aur woh her cheez per qadir hai
  57,3,Wohi pehlay hai aur wohi peechay wohi zahir hai aur wohi makhfi aur woh her cheez ko bakhoobi janney wala hai
  57,4,Wohi hai jiss ney aasmanon aur zamin ko cheh (6) din mein peda kiya phir arsh per mustawi hogaya Woh (Khoob) jaanta hai uss cheez ko zamin mein jaye aur jo uss say niklay aur jo aasmanoon say neechay aaye. aur jo kuch Charh ker uss mein jaye aur jahan kahin tum ho woh tumharay sath hai aur jo tum kerahey ho Allah dekh raha hai
  57,5,Aasmanoon ki aur zamin ki baadshahi ussi ki hai aur tamam kaam ussi ki taraf lotaye jatay hain
  57,6,Wohi raat ko din mein lejata hai aur wohi din ko raat mein dakhil kerdeta hai aur seenoon kay bhedon ka woh poora aalim hai
  57,7,Allah per aur uss kay raool per eman ley aao aur uss maal mein say kharch kero jiss mein Allah ney tumhen doosron ka janasheen banaya hai pus jo tum mein say eman leyen aur kheraat keren unhen boht bara sawab milay ga
  57,8,Tum ALLAH per eman kiyon nahi latay ? Halankay khud rasool tumhen apney rab per eman lanay ki dawat dey raha hai agar tum momin ho to who to tum say mazboot ehad-o-paymaan bhi ley chukka hai
  57,9,Woh (ALLAH) hi hai jo apney banday per wazeh aayaten utaarta hai takay who tumhen andheron say noor ki taraf ley jaye yaqeenan ALLAH taalaa tum per narmi kernay wala reham kernay wala hai
  57,10,kertay' darasal aasmanon our zamin ke meeress ka malik (tanha) Allah hi hai tum main say jin logo ney fatah say pehlay fi subilillah diya hai our qitaal kiya hai woh (doosron kay) barabar nahi bulkay unn say boht baray darjay kay hain jinhon nay fatah kay baad kheyraaten den our jahad kiyey haan bhalaee ka wada to Allah taalaaka unn sab say hai jo kuch tum ker rahey ho uss say Allah khabardaarhai
  57,11,Kon hai jo Allah taalaa ko achi tarah qarz dey phir Allah Taalaa issay uss kay liye barhata chala jaye our uss kay liye pasandeedah ajar sabit hojaye
  57,12,(Qayamat Kay) din tu dekhay ga kay momin mardo our orton ka noor unn kay aagay aagay our unkay dayen dor raha hoga aaj tumhen inn jannaton ki khushkhabri hai jinkay neechay nehren jaari hain jin main humesha ki rehaeesh hai yeh hai bari kaamyabi
  57,13,Uss din munafiq mard-o-orat eman walon say kahan gay kay humara intizar to kero kay hum bhi tumharay noor say kuch roshni hasil kerlen jawab diya jayega kay tum apney peechay lot jao our roshni talash kero phir inkay our unkay darmiyan aik deewar haaeel kerdi jayegi jiss main darwaaza bhi hoga uss kay androoni hissay main to rehmathogi our bahir ki taraf azab hoga
  57,14,Yeh chilla chilla ker unn say kahen gey kay kiya hum tumharay sath na thay woh kahengay kay haan thay to sahi lekin tum ney apney app ko fitnay mein phansa rakha tha our intizar mein hi rahey our shak-o-shuba kertay raheyour tumhen tumhari fazool tamannao ney dhokay mein hi rakha yahan tak kay Allah ka hukum aa phoncha our tumhen Allah kay baray mein dhoka denay walay ney dhokay mein hi rakha
  57,15,Algharz aaj tum say na fidya (aur na badla) qabool kiya jayega our na kafiron say tum (sab) ka thikana dozakh hai wohi tumhari rafiq hai our woh bura thikana hai
  57,16,Kiya abb tak eman walon kay liye waqt nahi aaya kay unkay dil zikar-e-elaahi say our our jo haqutar chuka hai uss say narum hojayen our unki tarah na hojayen jinhen unn say pehlay kitab di gaee thi phir job inn per aik zamana dorazguzer gaya to unkay dil sakht hogaye our inn mein boht say faasiq hain
  57,17,Yaqeen mano Allah hi zamin ko uss ki mot kay baad zinda kerdeta hai hum ney to tumharay liye apni aayaten biyan kerdin takay tum samjho
  57,18,Be-shak sadqa denay walay mard our sadqa denay wali orten our jo Allah ko khuloos kay sath qarz dey rahey hain unkay liye yeh barhaya jayega our unn kay liye pasandeedah ajar-o-sawab hai
  57,19,Allah our uskay rasool per jo eman rakhtay hain wohi log apney rab kay nazdeek siddiq our shaheed hain unkay liye unka ajar our unka noor hai our jo log kufur kertay hain our humari aayaton ko jhutlatay hain woh jahannomi hain
  57,20,Khoob jaan rakho kay duniya ki zindagi sirf khel tamasha zeenat aor aapas main fakhar (o-ghuroor) our maal-o-olad main aik ka doosary say apney aap ko ziyadah batlana jaisay barish aur iss ki padawaar kisanon ko achi maloom hota hai phir job woh khushk hojati hai to zard rang main iss ko tum dejhtey ho phir woh bilkul choora choora hojatai hai our aakhirat main sakht azab aur Allah ke maghfirat our razamandi hai our duniya ki zundagi ba-juz dhokay kay saman kay our kuch bhi to nahi
  57,21,(Aao) doro apney rab ki maghfirat ki taraf our uss jannat ki taraf jiss ki wussat kay barabar hai yeh unkay liye banaee gaee hai jo Allah per aur uskay rasoolon per eman rakhtay hain yeh Allah ka fazal hai jissay chahye dey aur Allah bara fazl wala hai
  57,22,Na koi museebat duniya main aati hai na (Khaas) tumhari jaanon main magar iss say pehlay kay hum usko peda keran woh aik khaas kitab main likhi hui hai yeh (kaam) Allah taalaa per (bilkul)aasan hai
  57,23,Takay tum apney say fol shuda kissi cheez per ranjeedah na hojoya kero our na attakerdah cheez per itra jao.our itranay walay shekhi khoron ko Allah pasand nhifarmata
  57,24,Jo (khud bhi) bulkul keren aur doosron ko (bhi) bulkhul ki taleem dea Suno! jo bhi main pheray Allah beyniaz aur sazawaar hamd-o-sana hai
  57,25,yaqeenan hum ney apney payghambaron ko khuli doleelen dey ker bheja our unkay sath kitab our meean nazilfarmaya. takay log adal per qaeem rahein aur hum ney lohey ko utara jiss mein sakht hebat-o-qooat hai aur logon kay liye aur bhi (boht say) faeeday hain aur iss liye bhi kay ALLAH jaan ley kay uski aur uss kay rasoolon ki madad bey dekhay kon kerta hai be-shak ALLAH qooat wala aur zabardast hai
  57,26,Be-shak hum ney nooh aur ibrahim (aleh-e-salam) ko (payghumber banaker) bheja aur hum ney inn dono ki olad mein payghumbari aur kitab jari rakhi to inn mein say kuch to raah yafta huye aur inn mein say aksar boht nafarman rahey
  57,27,Inn kay baad phir bhi hum apney rasoolon ko pay-dar-pay bhejtay rahey aur inn kay baad Essa bin mariyum(aleh-e-salam) ko bheja aur unhen injeel ata farmaee aur unn kay mannay walon kay dilon mein shafqat aur reham peda kerdiahaan rehbaniyat (tark-e-duniya) to un logon ney unn per issay wajib na kiya tha siwaye ALLAH ki raza joee kay so so unhon ney iss ki poori riyat na ki phir bhi hum ney unn mein say jo eman laye thay unhen unka ajar diya aur unn mein ziyadaah tar log nafarman hain
  57,28,Aey woh logon jo eman laye ho ALLAH say dartay raha kero aur uss kay rasool per eman lao ALLAH tumhen apni rehmat ka dohra hissa dey ga aur tumhen noor dey ga jiss ki roshni mein tum chalo gey phiro gey aur tumharay gunah bhi moaaf farma dey ga ALLAH bakshnay wala meharbaan hai
  57,29,yeh iss liye kay ehl-e-kitab jaan lein kay ALLAH kay fazal kay kissi hissay per bhi unhen ikhtiyar nahi aur yeh kay (sara) fazal ALLAH hi kay hath hai woh jissay chahye dey aur ALLAH hai hi bara fazal wala
  58,1,Yaqeenan Allah Taalaa ney uss aurat ki baat suni jo tujh say apney shoher kay baray mein takraar ker rahi thi aur Allah kay aagay shikayat ker rahi thi Allah Taalaa tum dono kay sawal-o-jawab sunn raha tha be-shak Allah Taalaa sunnay dekhney wala hai
  58,2,Tum mein say jo log apni biwiyon say zahaar kertay hain (yani unhen maa keh bethtay hain) woh dar asal unn ki maayen nahi bann jatin unn ki maayen to wohi hain jin kay batan say woh peda huye yaqeenan yeh log aik na maqool aur jhooti baat kehtay hain be-shak Allah Taalaa moaf kerney wala aur bakshney wala hai
  58,3,Jo log apni biwiyon say zahaar keren phir apni kahi hui baat say rujoo ker len to unn kay zimmay aapas mein aik doosray ko haath laganey say pehlay aik ghulam aazad kerna hai iss kay zariye tum naseehat kiye jatay ho aur Allah Taalaa tumharay tamam aemaal say ba khabar hai
  58,4,Haan jo shaks na paye uss kay zimmay do maheenon kay laga taar rozay hain iss say pehlay kay aik doosray ko haath lagayen aur jiss shaks ko yeh taqat bhi na ho uss per saathh (60) miskeenon ka khana khilana hai. Yeh iss liye kay tum Allah ki aur uss kay rasool ki hukum bardari kero yeh Allah Taalaa ki muqarrar kerda hadden hain aur kuffaar hi kay liye dard naak azab hai
  58,5,Be-shak jo log Allah aur uss kay rasool ki mukhalifat kertay hain woh zaleel kiye jayen gay jaisay unn say pehlay kay log zaleel kiye gaye thay aur be-shak hum wazeh aayaten utaar chuken hain aur kafiron kay liye to zillat wala azab hai
  58,6,Jiss din Allah Taalaa inn sab ko uthaye ga phir enhen unn kay kiye huye aemaal say aagah keray ga jissay Allah ney shumar ker rakha hai aur jissay yeh bhool gaye thay aur Allah Taalaa her cheez say waqif hai
  58,7,Kiya tu ney nahi dekha kay Allah aasmanon ki aur zamin ki her cheez say waqif hai. Teen aadmiyon ki sirgoshi nahi hoti magar Allah unn ka chotha hota hai na paanch ki magar unn ka chatha (6th) woh hota hai aur na iss say kum ki aur na ziyada ki magar woh sath hi hota hai jahan bhi woh hon phir qayamat kay din unhen unn ka aemaal say aagah keray ga be-shak Allah Taalaa her cheez say waqif hai
  58,8,Kiya tu ney unn logon ko nahi dekha? Jinhen kaana phoosi say rok diya gaya tha woh phir bhi iss rokay huye kaam ko doobara kertay hain aur aapas mein gunah ki aur zulm-o-ziyadti ki aur na farmaniy-e-payghumbar ki sirgoshiyan kertay hain aur jab teray pass aatay hain to tujhay inn lafzon mein salam kertay hain jin lafzon mein Allah Taalaa ney nahi kaha aur apney dil mein kehtay hain kay Allah Taalaa humen iss per jo hum kehtay hain saza kiyon nahi deta inn kay liye jahannum kafi (saza) hai jiss mein yeh jayen gay so woh bura thikana hai
  58,9,Aey eman walo! Tum jab sirgoshi kero to yeh sirgoshiyan gunah aur zulm (ziyadti) aur na farmaniy-e-payghumbar ki na hon bulkay neki aur perhezgari ki baaton per sirgoshi kero aur uss Allah say dartay raho jiss kay pass tum jama kiye jao gay
  58,10,(buri) sirgoshiyan pus shetani kaam hai jiss say eman daaron ko ranj phonchay. Go Allah Taalaa ki ijazat kay baghair woh enehn koi nuksan nahi phoncha sakta aur eman walon ko chahaiye kay woh Allah per bharosa rakhen
  58,11,Aey musalmano! Jab tum say kaha jaye kay majlison mein zara kushagi peda kero to tum jagah kushada kerdo Allah tumhen kushadgi dey ga aur jab kaha jaye kay uth kharay hojao to tum uth kharay hojao Allah Taalaa tum mein say unn logon kay jo eman laye hain aur jo ilm diye gaye hain darjay buland ker dey ga aur Allah Taalaa (her uss kaam say) jo tum ker rahey ho (khoob) khabardaar hai
  58,12,Aey musalmano! Jab tum rasool (PBUH) sau sirgoshi kerna chahao to apni sirgoshi say pehlay kuch sadqa dey diya kero yeh tumharay haq mein behtar hai haan agar na pao to be-shak Allah Taalaa bakshney wala meharban hai
  58,13,Kiya tum apni sirgoshi say pehlay sadqa nikalney say darr gaye? Pus jab tum ney na kiya aur Allah Taalaa ney bhi tumhen moaf farma diya to abb (ba khoobi) namazon ko qaeem rakho zakat detay raha kero aur Allah Taalaa ki aur uss kay rasool ki tabey daari kertay raho iss (sab) say Allah (khoob) khabardaar hai
  58,14,Kiya tu ney unn logon ko nahi dekha? Jinhon ney uss qom say dosti ki jin per Allah ghazab naak ho chuka hai na yeh (munafiq) tumharay hi hain na unn kay hain ba wajood ilm kay phir bhi jhoot per qasmen kha rahey hain
  58,15,Allah Taalaa ney inn kay liye sakht azab tayyar ker rakha hai tehqeeq yeh jo kuch ker rahey hain bura ker rahey hain
  58,16,Inn logon ney to apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai aur logon ko Allah ki raah say roktay hain inn kay liye ruswa kerney wala azab hai
  58,17,Inn kay maal aur inn ki aulad Allah kay haan inn kay kuch kaam na aayen gi. Yeh to jahannumi hain hamesha hi iss mein rahen gay
  58,18,Jiss din Allah Taalaa inn sab ko utha khara keray ga to yeh jiss tarah tumharay samney qasmen khatay hain (Allah Taalaa) kay samney bhi qasmen khaney lagen gay aur samjhen gay kay woh bhi kissi (daleel) per hain yaqeen mano kay be-shak wohi jhootay hain
  58,19,Inn per shetan ney ghalba hasil ker liya hai aur enhen Allah ka zikar bhula diya hai yeh shetani lashkar hai koi shak nahi kay shetani lashkar hi khasaray wala hai
  58,20,Be-shak Allah Taalaa ki aur uss kay rasool ki jo log mukhalifat kertay hain wohi log sab say ziyada zaleelon main hain
  58,21,Allah Taalaa likh chuka hai kay be-shak mein aur meray payghumbar rahen gay. Yaqeenan Allah Taalaa zor aawar aur ghalib hai
  58,22,Allah Taalaa per aur qayamat kay din per eman rakhney walon ko aap Allah aur uss kay rasool ki mukhalifat kerney walon say mohabbat rakhtay huye hergiz na payen gay go woh unn kay baap ya unn kay betay ya unn kay bhai ya unn kay kunbay (qabeelay) kay (aziz) hi kiyon na hon. Yehi log hain jin kay dilon mein Allah Taalaa ney eman likh diya hai aur jin ki taeed apni rooh say ki hai aur jinhen unn jannaton mein dakhil keray ga jin kay neechay nehren beh rahi hain jahan yeh hamesha rahen gay Allah inn say razi hai aur yeh Allah say khush hain yeh khudaee lashkar hai aagah raho be-shak Allah kay giroh walay hi kaamyaab log hain
  59,1,Aasmanon aur zamin ki her cheez Allah Taalaa ki paki biyan kerti hai aur woh ghalib ba hikmat hai
  59,2,Wohi hai jiss ney ehal-e-kitab mein say kafiron ko unn kay gharon say pehlay hashar kay waqt nikala tumhara gumaan (bhi) na tha kay woh niklen gay aur woh khud (bhi) samajh rahey thay kay unn kay (sangeen) qilay unhen Allah (kay azab) say bacha len gay pus unn per Allah (ka azab) aisi jagah say aa para kay unhen gumaan bhi na tha aur unn kay dilon mein Allah ney rob daal diya aur apney gharon ko apney hi haathon ujaar rahey thay aur musalmanon kay haathon (barbad kerwa rahey thay) pus aey aankhon walo! Ibrat hasil kero
  59,3,Aur agar Allah Taalaa ney inn per jila watni ko muqaddar na ker diya hota to yaqeenan enhen duniya mein azab deta aur aakhirat mein (to) inn kay liye aag ka azab hai hi
  59,4,Yeh iss liye kay enhon ney Allah Taalaa ki aur uss kay rasool ki mukhalifat ki aur jo bhi Allah ki mukhalifat keray ga to Allah Taalaa bhi sakht azab kerney wala hai
  59,5,Tum ney khujooron kay jo darakht kaat dalay ya jinhen tum ney unn ki jaron mein baqi rehney diya. Yeh sab Allah Taalaa kay farmaan say tha aur iss liye bhi kay fasiqon ko Allah Taalaa ruswa keray
  59,6,Aur inn ka jo maal Allah Taalaa ney apney rasool kay haath lagaya hai jiss per na to tum ney ghoray doraye hain aur na oont bulkay Allah Taalaa apney rasool ko jiss per chahaye ghalib ker deta hai aur Allah Taalaa her cheez per qadir hai
  59,7,Bastiyon walon ka jo (maal) Allah Taalaa tumharay laray bhiray baghair apney rasool kay haath lagaye woh Allah ka hai aur rasool ka aur qarabat walon ka aur yateemon miskeenon ka aur musafiron ka hai takay tumharay dolat mandon kay haath mein hi yeh maal gardish kerta na reh jaye aur tumhen jo kuch rasool dey ley lo aur jiss say rokay ruk jao aur Allah Taalaa say dartay raha kero yaqeenan Allah Taalaa sakht azab wala hai
  59,8,(fey kaa maal) unn mohajir miskeenon kay liye hai jo apney gharon say aur apney maalon say nikal diye gaye hain woh Allah kay fazal aur uss ki raza mandi kay talabgaar hain aur Allah Taalaa ki aur uss kay rasool ki madad kertay hain yehi raast baaz log hain
  59,9,Aur (unn kay liye) jinhon ney iss ghar mein (yani madina) aur eman mein inn say pehlay jagah bana li hai aur apni taraf hijrat ker kay aaney walon say mohabbat kertay hain aur mohajireen ko jo kuch dey diya jaye iss say woh apney dilon mein koi tangi nahi rakhtay bulkay khud apney upper enhen tarjeeh detay hain go khud ko kitni hi sakht haajat ho (baat yeh hai) kay jo bhi apney nafs kay bukhul say bachaya gaya wohi kaamyaab (aur baa murad) hai
  59,10,Aur (unn kay liye) jo inn kay baad aayen jo kahen gay kay aey huamray perwerdigar humen baksh dey aur humaray unn bhaiyon ko bhi jo hum say pehlay eman laa chukay hain aur eman daaron ki taraf say humaray dil mein keena (aur dushmani) naa daal aey humaray rab be-shak tu shafqat aur meharbani kerney wala hai
  59,11,Kiya tu ney munfiqon ko na dekha? Kay apney ehal-e-kitab kafir bhaiyon say kehtay hain kay agar tum jila watan kiye gaye to zaroor bil zaroor hum bhi tumharay sath nikal kharay hongay aur tumharay baray mein hum kabhi bhi kissi ki baat na maanen gay aur agar tum say jang ki jaye gi to ba khuda hum tumhari madad keren gay lekin Allah Taalaa gawahi deta hai kay yeh qata’an jhootay hain
  59,12,Agar woh jila watan kiye gaye to yeh unn kay sath na jayen gay aur agar inn say jang ki gaee yeh inn ki madad (bhi) na keren gay aur agar (bil farz) madad per aa bhi gaye to peeth pher ker (bhaag kharay) hon gay phir madad na kiye jayen gay
  59,13,(musalmano! Yaqeen mano) kay tumhari heybat inn kay dilon mein ba nisbat Allah ki heybat kay boht ziyada hai yeh iss liye kay yeh bey samajh log hain
  59,14,Yeh sab mill ker bhi tum say larr nahi saktay haan yeh aur baat hai kay qila band muqamaat mein hon ya deewaron ki aarh mein hon inn ki laraeeto inn mein aapas mein hi boht sakht hai go aap enhen mutahid samajh rahey hain lekin inn kay dil dar asal aik doosray say juda hain iss lie kay yeh bey aqal log hain
  59,15,Unn logon ki tarah jo inn say kuch hi pehlay guzray hain jinhon ney apney kaam ka wabal chakh liya aur jin kay liye alam naak azab (tayyar) hai
  59,16,Shetan ki tarah kay uss ney insan say kaha kufur ker jab woh kufur ker chuka to kehney laga mein to tujh say bari hun mein to Allah rab-ul-aalameen say darta hun
  59,17,Pus dono ka anjam yeh hua kay aatish (dozakh) mein hamesha kay liye gaye aur zalimon ki yehi saza hai
  59,18,Aey eman walon! Allah say dartay raho aur her shaks dekh (bhaal) ley kay kal (qayamat) kay wastay uss ney (aemaal ka) kiya (zakheera) bheja hai. Aur (her waqt) Allah say dartay raho Allah tumharay sab aemaal say ba khabar hai
  59,19,Aur tum unn logon ki tarah mat ho jana jinhon ney Allah (kay ehkaam) ko bhula diya to Allah ney bhi unhen apni jano say ghafil ker diya aur aisay hi log na farmaan (faasiq) hotay hain
  59,20,Ehal-e-naar aur ehal-e-jannat (ba hum) barabar nahi. Jo ehal-e-jannat hain wohi kaamyaab hain (aur jo ehal-e-naar hain woh na kaam hain)
  59,21,Agar hum iss quran ko kissi pahar per utartay to tu dekhta kay khof-e-elahee say woh pust ho ker tukray tukray ho jata hum inn misalon ko logon kay samney biyan kertay hain takay woh ghor-o-fiker keren
  59,22,Wohi Allah hai jiss kay siwa koi mabood nahi chupay khulay ka jannay wala meharban aur reham kerney wala
  59,23,Wohi Allah hai jiss kay siwa koi mabood nahi badshah nihayat pak sab aeybon say saaf aman denay wala nighehbaan ghalib zor aawar aur baraee wala pak hai Allah unn cheezon say jinhen yeh uss ka shareek banatay hain
  59,24,Wohi Allah hai peda kerney wala wujood bakshney wala soorat bananey wala ussi kay liye (nihayat) achay naam hain her cheez khuwa woh aasman mein ho khuwa zamin mein ho uss ki paki biyan kerti hai aur wohi ghalib hikmat wala hai
  60,1,Aey woh logo jo eman laye ho! Meray aur (khud) apney dushmanon ko apna dost na banao tum to dosti say unn ki taraf payghaam bhejtay ho aur woh iss haq kay sath jo tumharay pass aa chuka hai kufur kertay hain payghumbar ko aur khud tumhen bhi mehaz iss waja say jila watan kertay hain kay tum apney rab per eman rakhtay ho agar tum meri raah mein jihad kay liye aur meri raza mandi ki talab mein nikaltay ho ( to inn say dostiyan na kero) tum inn kay pass mohabbat ka paygham posheeda posheeda bhejtay ho aur mujhay khoob maloom hai jo tum ney chupaya aur woh bhi jo tum ney zahir kiya tum mein say jo bhi iss kaam ko keray ga woh yaqeenan raah-e-raast say behak jaye ga
  60,2,Agar woh tum per kahin qaboo paa len to woh tumharay (khulay) dushman ho jayen aur buraee kay sath tum per dast darazi aur zaban darazi kerney lagen aur (dil say) chahaney lagen kay tum bhi kufur kerney lagg jao
  60,3,Tumhari qarabaten rishtay dariyan aur aulad tumhen qayamat kay din kaam na aayen gi Allah Taalaa tumharay darmiyan faisla ker dey ga aur jo kuch tum ker rahey ho ussay Allah khoob dekh raha hai
  60,4,(musalmano!) tumharay liye hazrat ibrahim mein aur unn kay sathiyon mein behtareen namoona hai jabkay unn sab ney apni qom say bar mala keh diya kay hum tum say aur jin jin ki tum Allah kay siwa ibadat kertay ho unn sab say bilkul bey zaar hain. Hum tumharay (aqaeed kay) munkir hain jab tak tum Allah ki wahadaniyat per eman na lao hum mein tum mein hamesha kay liye bughz-o-adawat zahir hogaee lekin ibrahim ki itni baat apney baap say hui thi kay mein tumharay liye istaghfaar zaroor keroon ga aur tumharay liye mujhay Allah kay samney kissi cheez ka ikhtiyar kuch bhi nahi. Aey humaray perwerdigar tujhi per hum ney bharosa kiya hai aur teri hi taraf rujoo kertay hain aur teri hi tarf lotna hai
  60,5,Aey humaray rab! Tu humen kafiron ki aazmaeesh mein na daal aur aey humaray paalney walay humari khataon ko bakhsh dey be-shak tu hi ghalib hikmat wala hai
  60,6,Yaqeenan tumharay liye inn mein acha namoona (aur umdah pairwi hai khaas ker) her uss shaks kay liye jo Allah ki aur qayamat kay din ki mulaqat ki umeed rakhta ho aur agar koi roo gardani keray to Allah Taalaa bilkul bey niaz hai aur saza waar hamd-o-sana hai
  60,7,Kiya ajab hai kay un qarib hi Allah Taalaa tum mein aur tumharay dushmanon mein mohabbat peda ker dey. Allah ko sab qudraten hain aur Allah (bara) ghafoor raheem hai
  60,8,Jin logon ney tum say deen kay baray mein laraee nahi lari aur tumhen jila watan nahi kiya unn kay sath salook-o-ehsan kerney aur munsifana bhalay bartao kerney say Allah Taalaa tumhen nahi rokta bulkay Allah Taalaa to insaf kerney walon say mohabbat kerta hai
  60,9,Allah Taalaa tumhen sirf unn logon ki mohabbat say rokta hai jinhon ney tum say deen kay baray mein laraiyan laren aur tumhen des nikalay diye aur des nikala denay walon ki madad ki jo log aisay kuffaar say mohabbat keren woh (qata’an) zalim hain
  60,10,Aey eman walo! Jab tumharay pass momin aurten hijrat ker kay aayen to tum unn ka imtehan lo. Dar asal unn kay eman ko ba khoobi janney wala to Allah hi hai lekin agar woh tumhen eman waliyan maloom hon to abb tum enhen kafiron ki taraf wapis na kero yeh unn kay liye halal nahi na woh inn kay liye halal hain aur jo kharach inn kafiron ka hua ho woh unhen ada kerdo inn aurton ko unn kay mehar dey ker inn say nikkah ker lenay mein tum per koi gunah nahi aur kafir aurton ki namoos apney qabzay mein na rakho aur jo kuch tum ney kharach kiya ho maang lo aur jo kuch inn kafiron ney kharach kiya ho woh bhi maang len yeh Allah ka faisla hai jo tumharay darmiyan ker raha hai Allah Taalaa baray ilm (aur) hikmat wala hai
  60,11,Aur agar tumhari koi biwi tumharay haath say nikal jaye aur kafiron kay pass chali jaye phir tumhen iss kay badlay ka waqt mill jaye to jin ki biwiyan chali gaeen hain unhen unn kay ikhrajaat kay barabar ada kerdo aur uss Allah Taalaa say dartay rahi jiss per tum eman rakhtay ho
  60,12,Aey payghumbar! Jab musalman aurten aap say inn baaton per bait kerney aayen kay woh Allah kay sath kissi ko shareek na keren gi chori na keren gi zina kaari na keren gi apni aulad ko naa maar dalen gi aur koi aisa bohtaan na bandhay gi jo khud apney haathon pairon kay sath gharr len aur kissi nek kaam mein teri bey hukmi na keren gi to aap inn say bait ker liya keren aur inn kay liye Allah say maghfirat talab keren be-shak Allah bakshney aur moaf kerney wala hai
  60,13,Aey musalmano! Tum uss qom say dosti na rakho jin per Allah ka ghazab nazil ho chuka hai jo aakhirat say iss tarah mayyus ho chukay hain jaisay kay murda ehal-e-qabar say kafir na umeed hain
  61,1,Zamin-o-aasman ki her her cheez Allah Taalaa ki paki biyan kerti hai aur wohi ghalib hikmat wala hai
  61,2,Aey eman walo! Tum woh baat kiyon kehtay ho jo kertay nahi
  61,3,Tum jo kertay nahi uss ka kehna Allah Taalaa ko sakht na pasand hai
  61,4,Be-shak Allah Taalaa unn logon say mohabbat kerta hai jo uss ki raah mein saff basta jihad kertay hain goya woh seesa pilaee hui emaarat hain
  61,5,Aur (yaad kero) jabkay musa ney apni qom say kaha aey meri qom kay logo! Tum mujhay kiyon sata rahey ho halankay tumhen (ba khoobi) maloom hai kay mein tumhari janib Allah ka rasool hun pus jab woh log tairhay hi rahey to Allah ney unn kay dilon ko (aur) tairhaa ker diya aur Allah Taalaa na farman qom ko hidayat nahi deta
  61,6,Aur jab marium kay betay essa ney kaha aey (meri qom) bani israeel! Mein tum sab ki taraf Allah ka rasool hun mujh say pehlay ki kitab toraat ki mein tasdeeq kerney wala hun aur apney baad aaney walay aik rasool ki mein tumhen khushkhabri sunaney wala hun jin ka naam ahmed hai phir jab woh unn kay pass khuli daleelen laye to yeh kehney lagay yeh to khula jadoo hai
  61,7,Uss shaks say ziyada zalim aur kaun hoga jo Allah per jhoot (iftra) bandhay halankay woh islam ki taraf bulaya jata hai aur Allah aisay zalimon ko hidayat nahi kerta
  61,8,Woh chahtay hain kay Allah kay noor ko apney mun say bujha den aur Allah apney noor ko kamal tak phonchaney wala hai go kafir bura manen
  61,9,Wohi hai jiss ney apney rasool ko hidayat aur sacha deen dey ker bheja takay ussay aur tamam mazaahib per ghalib ker dey agar cheh mushrikeen na khush hon
  61,10,Aey eman walo! Kiya mein tumhen woh tijarat batla doon jo tumhen dard naak azab say bacha ley
  61,11,Allah Taalaa per aur uss kay rasool per eman lao aur Allah ki raah mein apney maal aur apni jaanon say jihad kero. Yeh tumharay liye behtar hai agar tum mein ilm ho
  61,12,Allah Taalaa tumharay gunah moaf farma dey ga aur tumhen unn jannaton mein dakhil keray ga jin kay neechay nehren jari hongi aur saaf suthray gharon mein jo jannat adan mein hon gay yeh boht bari kaamyabi hai
  61,13,Aur tumhen aik doosri (nemat) bhi dey ga jisay tum chahtay ho woh Allah ki madad aur jald fatah yaabi hai eman walon ko khushkhabri dey do
  61,14,Aey eman walo! Tum Allah key madadgar bann jao. Jiss tarah hazrat marium kay betay hazrat essa ney hawariyon say farmaya kay kaun hai jo Allah ki raah mein mera madadgar baney? Hawariyon ney kaha hum Allah ki raah mein madadgar hain pus bani israeel mein say aik jamat to eman laee aur aik jamat ney kufur kiya tum hum ney mominon ki unn kay dushman kay muqabley mein madad ki pus woh ghalib aagaye
  62,1,(saari cheezen) jo aasmanon aur zamin mein hain Allah Taalaa ki paki biyan kerti hain (jo) badshah nihayat pak (hai) ghalib-o-ba hikmat
  62,2,Wohi hai jiss ney na khuanda logon mein inn hi mein say aik rasool bheja jo enhen uss ki aayaten parh ker sunata hai aur inn ko pak kerta hai aur enhen kitab-o-hikmat sikhata hai. Yaqeenan yeh iss say pehlay khuli gumrahi mein thay
  62,3,Aur doosron kay liye bhi unhi mein say jo abb tak inn say nahi milay aur wohi ghalib ba hikmat hai
  62,4,Yeh Allah ka fazal hai jissay chahaye apna fazal dey aur Allah Taalaa boht baray fazal ka maalik hai
  62,5,Jin logon ko toraat per amal kerney ka hukum diya gaya phir unhon ney uss per amal nahi kiya unn ki misal uss gadhay ki say hai jo boht si kitaben laaday ho. Allah ki baaton ko jhutlaney walon ki bari buri misal hai aur Allah (aisay) zalim qom ko hidayat nahi deta
  62,6,Keh dijiye kay aey yahudiyo! Agar tumhara daawa hai kay tum Allah kay dost ho doosray logon kay siwa to tum maut ki tamanna kero agar tum sachay ho
  62,7,Yeh kabhi bhi maut ki tamanna na keren gay ba waja unn aemaal kay jo apney aagay apney haathon bhej rakhay hain aur Allah zalimon ko khoob janta hai
  62,8,Keh dijiye kay jiss maut say tum bhagtay phirtay ho woh to tumhen phonch ker rahey gi pohir tum sab chupay khulay kay jannay walay (Allah) ki taraf lotaye jao gay aur woh tumhen tumharay kiye huye tamam kaam batla dey ga
  62,9,Aey woh logo jo eman laye ho! Jummay kay din namaz ki azan di jaye to tum Allah kay ziker kay taraf dor paro aur khareed-o-farokht chor do. Yeh tumharay haq mein boht hi behtar hai agar tum jantay ho
  62,10,Phir jab namaz ho chukay to zamin mein phel jao aur Allah ka fazal talash kero takay tum falah paa lo
  62,11,Aur jab koi soda biktay dekhen ya koi tamasha nazar aajaye to uss ki taraf dortay jatay hain aur aap ko khara hi chor detay hain aap keh dijiye kay Allah kay pass jo hai woh khel aur tijarat say behtar hai. Aur Allah Taalaa behtareen rozi rasan hai
  63,1,Tumharay pass jab munafiq aatay hain to kehtay hain kay hum iss baat kay gawah hain kay be-shak aap Allah kay rasool hain aur Allah janta hai yaqeenan aap uss kay rasool hain aur Allah gawahi deta hai kay yeh munafiq qata’an jhootay hain
  63,2,Enhon ney apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai pus Allah ki raah say ruk gaye be-shak bura hai woh kaam jo yeh ker rahey hain
  63,3,Yeh iss sabab say hai kay yeh eman laa ker phir kafir hogaye pus inn kay dilon per mohar ker di gaee abb yeh nahi samajhtay
  63,4,Jab aap enhen dekh len to inn kay jism aap ko khushnuma maloom hon yeh jab baaten kerney lagen to aap inn ki baaton per (apna) kaan lagayen goya kay yeh lakriyan hain deewar kay shaharay lagee huin her (sakht) aawaz ko apney khilaf samajhtay hain yehi haqeeqi dushman hain inn say bacho Allah enhen ghaarat keray kahan say phiray jatay hain
  63,5,Aur jab inn say kaha jata hai aao tumharay liye Allah kay rasool istaghfaar keren to apney sir matkatay hain aur aap dekhen gay kay woh takabbur kertay huye ruk jatay hain
  63,6,Inn kay haq mein aap ka istaghfaar kerna aur na kerna dono barabar hai Allah Taalaa enhen hergiz na bakshay ga be-shak Allah Taalaa (aisay) na farmaan logon ko hidayat nahi deta
  63,7,Yehi woh log hain jo kehtay hain kay jo log rasool-lullah kay pass hain unn per kuch kharach na kero yahan tak kay woh idhar udhar ho jayen aur aasman-o-zamin kay kul khazaney Allah Taalaa ki milkiyat hain lekin yeh munfiq bey samajh hain
  63,8,Yeh kehtay hain kay agar hum abb lot ker madina jayen gay to izzat wala wahan say zillat walay ko nikal dey ga. Suno! Izzat to sirf Allah Taalaa kay liye aur uss kay rasool kay liye aur eman daaron kay liye hai lekin yeh munafiq jantay nahi
  63,9,Aey musalmano! Tumharay maal aur tumhari auladen tumhen Allah kay ziker say ghafil na ker den aur jo aisa keren woh baray hi ziyan kaar log hain
  63,10,Aur jo kuch hum ney tumhen dey rakha hai uss mein say (humari raah mein) iss say pehaly kharach kero kay tum mein say kissi ko maut aajaye to kehney lagay aey meray perwerdigar! Mujhay to thori dare ki mohlat kiyon nahi deta? Kay mein sadqa keroon aur nek logon mein say ho jaon
  63,11,Aur jab kissi ka muqarrar waqt aajata hai phir ussay Allah Taalaa hergiz mohlat nahi deta aur jo kuch tum kertay ho uss say Allah Taalaa bakhoobi ba khabar hai
  64,1,Tamam cheez jo aasmanon aur zamin mein hain Allah ki paki biyan kerti hain ussi ki saltanat hai aur ussi ki tareef hai aur woh her her cheez per qadir hai
  64,2,Ussi ney tumhen peda kiya hai so tum mein say baazay to kafir hain aur baaz eman walay hain aur jo kuch tum ker rahey ho Allah Taalaa khoob dekh raha hai
  64,3,Ussi ney aasmanon ko aur zamin ko adal-o-himat say peda kiya ussi ney tumhari sooraten banaeen aur boht achi banaeen aur ussi ki taraf lotna hai
  64,4,Woh aasman-o-zamin ki her her cheez ka ilm rakhta hai aur jo kuch tum chupao aur jo zahir kero woh (sab ko) janta hai. Allah to seenon ki baaton tak ko jannay wala hai
  64,5,Kiya tumharay pass iss say pehlay kay kafiron ki khabar nahi phonchi? Jinhon ney apney aemaal ka wabaal chakh liya aur jin kay liye dard naak azab hai
  64,6,Yeh iss liey kay unn kay pass unn kay rasool wazeh dalaeel ley ker aaye to unhon ney keh diya kay kiya insan humari rehnumaee keray ga? Pus inkar ker diya aur mun pher liya aur Allah ney bhi bey niazi ki aur Allah to hi boht bey niaz sab khoobiyon wala
  64,7,Inn kafiron ney khayal kiya hai kay doobara zinda na kiye jayen gay aap key dijiye kay kiyon nahi Allah ki qasam! Tum zaroor doobara uthaye jao gay phir jo tum ney kiya hai uss ki khabar diye jaogay aur Allah per yeh bilkul aasan hai
  64,8,So tum Allah per aur uss kay rasool per aur uss noor per jissay hum ney nazil farmaya hai eman laao aur Allah Taalaa tumharay her amal per ba-khabar hai
  64,9,Jiss din tum sab ko uss jama honey kay din jama keray ga wohi din hai haar jeet ka aur jo shaks Allah per eman laa ker nek amal keray Allah uss say uss ki buraiyan door ker dey ga aur ussay jannaton mein dakhil keray ga jin kay neechay nehren beh rahi hain jin mein woh hamesha hamesha rahen gay. Yehi boht bari kaamyabi hai
  64,10,Aur jin logon ney kufur kiya aur humari aayaton ko jhutlaya wohi (sab) jahannumi hain (jo) jahannum mein hamesha rahen gay woh boht bura thikana hai
  64,11,Koi museebat Allah ki ijazat kay baghair nahi phonch sakti jo Allah per eman laye Allah uss kay dil ko hidayat deta hai aur Allah her cheez ko khoob jannay wala hai
  64,12,(logo) Allah ka kehna mano aur rasool ka kehna mano. Pus agar tum aeyraaz kero to humaray rasool kay zimmay sirf saaf saaf phoncha dena hai
  64,13,Allah kay siwa koi mabood-e-bar haq nahi aur mominon ko Allah hi per tawakkal rakhna chahaiye
  64,14,Aey eman walo! Tumhari baaz biwiyan aur baaz bachay tumharay dushman hain pus inn say hoshiyaar rehna aur agar tum moaf kerdo aur dar-guzar ker jao aur bakhsh do to Allah Taalaa baskshney wala meharban hai
  64,15,Tumharay maal aur aulad to sirasir tumahri aazmaeesh hain aur boht bara ajar Allah kay pass hai
  64,16,Pus jahan tak tum say ho sakay Allah say dartay raho aur suntay aur maantay chalay jao aur Allah ki raah mein kheyraat kertay raho jo tumhara liye behtar hai aur jo shaks apney nafs ki hirss say mehfooz rakha jaye wohi kaamyab hai
  64,17,Agar tum Allah ko acha qarz do gay (yani uss ki raah mein kharach kero gay) to woh ussay tumharay liye barhata jaye ga aur tumharay gunah bhi moaf farma dey ga Allah bara qadar daan bara burd baar hai
  64,18,Woh posheeda aur zahir ka jannay wala hai zabardast hikmat wala (hai)
  65,1,Aey nabi! (apni ummat say kaho kay) jab tum apni biwiyon ko tallaq dena chahao to unn ki iddat (kay dino kay aaghaaz) mein unhen tallaq do aur iddat ka hisab rakho aur Allah say jo tumhara perwerdigar hai dartay raho na tum enhen inn kay gharon say nikalo aur na woh (khud) niklen haan yeh aur baat hai kay woh khuli buraee ker bethen yeh Allah ki muqarrar kerda hadden hain jo shaks Allah ki haddon say aagay barh jaye uss ney yaqeenan apney upper zulm kiya tum nahi jantay shayad iss kay baad Allah Taalaa koi naee baat peda ker dey
  65,2,Pus jab yen aurten apni iddat poori kerney kay qarib phonch jayen to unhen ya to qaeeday kay mutabiq apney nikkah mein rehney do ya dastoor kay mutabiq enhen alag kerdo aur aapas mein do aadil shakson ko gawah kerlo aur Allah ki raza mandi kay liye theek theek gawahi do. Yehi hai woh jiss ki naseehat ussay ki jati hai jo Allah per aur qayamat kay din per eman rakhta ho aur jo shaks Allah say darta hai Allah uss kay liye chutkaray ki shakal nikal deta hai
  65,3,Aur ussay aisi jagah say rozi deta hai jiss ka ussay guman bhi na ho aur jo shaks Allah per tawakkal keray ga Allah ussay kafi hoga. Allah Taalaa apna kaam poora ker kay hi rahey ga. Allah Taalaa ney her cheez ka aik andaza muqarrar ker rakha hai
  65,4,Tumhari aurton mein say jo aurten hez say na umeed ho gaee hon agar tumhen shuba ho to unn ki muddat teen maheeney hai aur unn ki bhi jinhen hez aana shuroo hi na hua ho aur hamila aurton ki iddat unn kay waza-e-hamal hai aur jo shaks Allah Taalaa say daray ga Allah uss kay (her) kaam mein aasani ker dey ga
  65,5,Yeh Allah ka hukum hai jo uss ney tumhari taraf utara hai aur jo shaks Allah say daray ga Allah uss kay gunah mita dey ga aur ussay bara bhari ajar dey ga
  65,6,Tum apni taqat kay mutabiq jahan tum rehtay ho wahan inn (tallaq wali) aurton ko rakho aur enhen tang kerney kay liye takleef na phonchao aur agar woh hamal say hon to jab tak bacha peda ho lay enhen kharach detay raha kero phir agar tumharay kehney say wohi doodh pilayen to tum enehn inn ki ujrat dey do aur ba-hum munasib tor per mashwara ker liya kero aur agar tum aapas mein kash-ma-kash kero to iss kay kehney say koi aur doodh pilaye gi
  65,7,Kushadgi walay ko apni kushadgi say kharach kerna chahaiye aur jiss per uss kay rizq ki tangi ki gaee ho ussay chahaiye kay jo kuch Allah ney ussay dey rakha hai ussi mein say (apni hasb-e-heysiyat) dey kissi shaks ko Allah takleef nahi deta magar utni hi jitni taqat ussay dey rakhi hai Allah tangi kay baad aasani aur faraghat bhi ker dey ga
  65,8,Aur boht si basti walon ney apney rab kay hukum say aur uss kay rasoolon say sir taabi ki aur hum ney bhi unn say sakht hisab kiya aur unhen azab diya unn dekha (sakht) azab
  65,9,Pus unhon ney apney kartoot ka maza chakh liya aur anjam kaar unn ka khasara hi hua
  65,10,Unn kay liye Allah Taalaa ney sakht azab tayyar ker rakha hai pus Allah say daro aey aqal mand eman walo. Yaqeenan Allah ney tumhari taraf naseehar utaar di hai
  65,11,(yani) rasool jo tumhen Allah kay saaf saaf ehkaam parh ker sunata hai takay unn logon ko jo eman layen aur nek amal keren woh tareekiyon say roshni ki taraf ley aaye aur jo shaks Allah per eman laye aur nek amal keray Allah ussay aisi jannaton mein dakhil keray ga jiss kay neechay nehren jari hain jin mein yeh hamesha hamesha rahen gay. Be-shak Allah ney ussay behtareen rozi dey rakhi hai
  65,12,Allah woh hai jiss ney saat aasaman banaye aur issi kay misil zaminen bhi. Iss ka hukum inn kay darmiyan utarta hai takay tum jaan lo kay Allah her cheez per qadir hai aur Allah Taalaa ney her cheez ko ba-aetbaar ilm gher rakha hai
  66,1,Aey nabi! Ji ss cheez ko Allah ney aap kay liye halal ker diya hai ussay aap kiyon haram kertay hain? (Kiya) aap apni biwiyon ki raza mandi hasil kerna chahatay hain aur Allah bakhshney wala reham kerney wala hai
  66,2,Tehqeeq kay Allah Taalaa ney tumharay liye qasmon ka khol daalna muqarrar ker diya hai aur Allah Taalaa tumhara kaar saaz hai aur wohi (pooray) ilm wala hikmat wala hai
  66,3,Aur yaad ker jab nabi ney apni baaz aurton say aik posheeda baat kahi pus jab uss ney uss baat ki khabar ker di aur Allah ney apney nabi ko iss per aagah ker diya to nabi ney thori si baat to bata di aur thori si taal gaye phir jab nabi ney apni biwi ko yeh baat bataee to woh kehnay lagi iss ki khabar aap ko kiss ney di. Kaha sab jannay walay poori khabar rakhney walay Allah ney mujhay yeh batlaya hai
  66,4,(aey nabi ki dono biwiyo!) agar tum dono Allah kay samney tauba kerlo (to boht behtar hai) yaqeenan tumharay dil jhuk paren hain aur agar tum nabi kay khilaf aik doosray ki madad kero gi pus yaqeenan uss ka kaar saaz Allah hai aur jibraeel hain aur nek ehal-e-eman aur inn kay ilawa farishtay bhi madad kerney walay hain
  66,5,Agar (woh) payghumbar tumhen tallaq dey den to boht jald enhen inn ka rab! Tumharay badlay tum say behtar biwiyan inayat farmaye ga jo islam waliyan eman waliyan tauba kerney waliyan ibadat baja laaney waliyan rozay rakhney waliyan hongi baiwa aur kanwariyan
  66,6,Aey eman walo! Tum apney aap ko aur apney ghar walon ko uss aag say bachao jiss ka endhan insan hain aur pathar jiss per sakht dil mazboot farishtay muqarrar hain jinhen jo hukum Allah Taalaa deta hai uss ki na farmani nahi kertay bulkay jo hukum diya jaye baja laatay hain
  66,7,Aey kafiro! Aaj tum uzur aur bahana mat kero. Tumhen sirf tumharay kartoot ka badla diya jaraha hai
  66,8,Aey eman walo! Tum Allah kay samney sachi khalis tauba kero. Qareeb hai kay tumhara rab tumharay gunah door kerday aur tumhen aisi jannaton mein dakhil keray jin kay neechay nehren jari hain. Jiss din Allah Taalaa nabi ko aur eman daron ko jo inn kay sath hain ruswa na keray ga. Inn ka noor inn kay samney aur inn kay dayen dor raha hoga. Yeh duayen kertay hongay aey humaray rab humen kaamil noor ata farma aur humen bakhsh dey yaqeenan tu her cheez per qadir hai
  66,9,Aey nabi! Kafiron aur munafiqon say jihad kero aur inn per sakhti kero inn kay thikana jahannum hai aur woh boht buri jagah hai
  66,10,Allah Taalaa ney kafiron kay liye nooh ki aur loot ki biwi ki misal biyan farmaee yeh dono humaray bandon mein say do (shaista aur) nek bandon kay ghar mein thin phir unn ki enhon ney khayanat ki pus woh dono (nek banday) inn say Allah kay (kissi azab ko) na rok sakay aur hukum dey diya gaya (aey aurton) dozakh mein janey walon kay sath tum dono bhi chali jao
  66,11,Aur Allah Taalaa ney eman walon kay liye firaon ki biwi ki misal biyan farmaee jabkay uss ney dua ki aey meray rab! Meray liye apney pass jannat mein muqam bana aur mujhay firaon say aur uss kay amal say bacha aur mujhay zalim logon say khulasi dey
  66,12,Aur (misal biyan farmaee) marium bint-e-imran ki jiss ney apney namoos ki hifazat ki phir hum ney apni taraf say uss mein jaan phook di aur (marium) uss ney apney rab ki baaton aur uss ki kitabon ki tasdeeq ki aur ibadat guzaron mein say thi
  67,1,Boht babarkat hai woh (Allah) jiss kay hath mein badshaee hai aur jo her cheez per qudrat rakhnay wala hai
  67,2,Jiss nay mot aur hayat ko iss liye peda kiya kay tumhen aazmaye kay tum mein say achay kaam kon kerta hai aur woh ghalib (aur) bakhshnay wala hai
  67,3,Jiss ney saat aasman uper talay banaye (to aey dekhnay walay) Allah Rehman ki pedaish mein koi bey-zaabtagi na dekhay ga
  67,4,Doobara (nazren daal ker) dekhley kiya koi shigaaf bhi nazar aaraha hai
  67,5,Phir dohra ker do do baar dekhley teri nigah teri taraf zalil(o-aajiz) hoker thaki hui lot aayegi.Be-shak hum ney aasman duniya ko chiraghon (sitaron) say aarasta kiya aur enehn shetanon kay maarnay ka zariya banadiya aur shetanon kay liye hum ney (dozakh ka jalanay wala) azab tayyar kerdiya
  67,6,Aur apnay rab kay sath kafur kernay walon kay liye jahannum ka azab hai aur woh kiya hi buri jagah hai
  67,7,Jab iss mein yeh daaley jayengey to iss ki baray zor ki aawazen sunen gey aur woh josh maar rahi hogi
  67,8,Qareeb hai kay (abhi) gussay kay maaray phat jaye jab kabhi iss mein koi giroh dala jayega uss say jahannum kay daroghay poochen gey kay kiya tumharay pass daranay wala koi nahi aaya tha
  67,9,Woh jawab dengey kay be-shak aaya tha lekin hum ney ussay jhutlaya aur hum ney kaha kay Allah taalaa ney kuch bhi naazil nahi farmaya tum boht bari gumrahi mein hi ho
  67,10,Aur kahen gey kay agar hum suntay hotay ya aqal rakhtay hotay to dozakhiyon mein (shareek) na hotay
  67,11,Pus unho ney apney jurum ka iqbal kerlia abb yeh dozakhi dafa hon (door hon)
  67,12,Be-shak jo log apnay perwerdigaar say ghaeebana tor per dartay rehtay hain unkay liye bakhhsish hai aur bara sawab hai
  67,13,Tum apni baton ko chupao ya zahir kero woh to seenon ki posheedgiyon ko bhi bakhoobi jaanta hai
  67,14,Kiya wohi na janay jiss nay peda kiya? phir woh bareek been aur bakhabar bhi ho
  67,15,Woh zaat jiss ney tumharay liye zamin ko past-o-mutee kerdia takay tum uss ki raahon mein chaltay phirtay raho aur Allah ki roziyan khao (piyo) ussi ki taraf (tumhen) ji ker uth khara hona hai
  67,16,Kiya tum iss baat say bey khof hogaye ho kay aasmanon wala tumhen zamin mein dhansa dey aur achanak zamin laraznay lagay
  67,17,Ya kiya tum iss baat say nadar hogaye ho kay aasmanon wala tum per pathar barsa dey? Phir to tumhen maloom ho hi jayega kay mera darna kaisa tha
  67,18,Aur inn say pehlay logon ney bhi jhutlaya tha to dekho inn per mera azab kaisa kuch hua
  67,19,Kiya yeh apnay uper per kholay huye aur (kabhi kabhi) sametay huye(urnay walay) parindon ko nahi dekhtay enhen (Allah) Rehman hi (hawa-o-faza mein) thaamay huye hai. be-shak her cheez uski nigah mein hai
  67,20,Siwaye Allah kay tumhara woh konsa lashkar hai jo tumhari madad kersakay kafir to sarasar dhokay hi mein hain
  67,21,Agar Allah taalaa apni rozi rok ley to batao kon hai jo phir tumhen rozi dey ga? bulkay (kafir) to sirkashi aur bidaknay per arr gaye hain
  67,22,Acha woh shaks zada hidayat wala hai jo apnay mun kay bal ondha hoker chalay ya woh jo seedha (peron kay bal) raah-e-raast per chala ho
  67,23,kehdijiye kay wohi (Allah) ahi jiss ney tumhen peda aur tumharay kaan aackhen aur dil banaye tum boht hi kum shukerguzari kertay ho
  67,24,Kehdijiye! kay wohi hai jiss ney tumhen zamin mein pehla diya aur usski taraf tum ikhattay kiye jaogey
  67,25,(Kafir) poochtay hain kay woh wada kab zahir hoga agar tum sachay ho (to batao)
  67,26,Aap kehdijiye kay iss ka ilm to Allah hi ko hai mein to sirf khulay tor per aagah kerdenay wala hon
  67,27,Jab yeh log iss waday ko qareeb tar paalen gey uss waqt unn kafiron kay chehray bigar jayen gey aur kehdia jayega kay yehi hai jissay tum talab kiya kertay thay
  67,28,Aap kehdijiye acha agar mujhay aur meray saathiyonko Allah taalaa halak kerdey ya hum per reham keray (bahar sooratyeh to batao) kay kafirron ko dardnaak azab say kon bachaye ga
  67,29,Aap kehdijiye! kay wohi Rehman hai hum to iss per eman la chukay aur issi per humara bharosa hai tumhenunqareeb maloom hojayega kay sareeh gumrahee mein kon hai
  67,30,Aap keh dijiye !kay acha yeh to batao kay agar tumharay (peenay ka) paani zamin mein utar jaye to kon hai jo tumharay liye nithra hua paani laye
  68,1,Noon qasam hai qalam ki aur uss ki jo kuch kay who (farishtay) likhtay hain
  68,2,Tu apany rab kay fazal say deewana nhai hai
  68,3,Aur be-shak teray liye bey inteha ajar hai
  68,4,Aur be-shak tu both baray (umda) ikhlaq per hai
  68,5,Pus abb tub hi dekhlega aur yeh bhi dekh len gay
  68,6,Kay tum main say kon fitnay mein pera hua hai
  68,7,Be-shak tera rab apni raah say behaknay walon ko khoob jaanta hai aur wohraah yafta logon ko tu bakhoobi jaanta hai
  68,8,Pus to jhutlanay walon kin a maan
  68,9,who to chahtay hain kay tu zara dheela ho to yeh bhi dheelay par jayen
  68,10,Aur tu kissi aisay shaks ka bhi kaha na manna jo ziyada qasmen khanay wala
  68,11,Beywaqar’ qammena aibgo chughalkhor
  68,12,Bhalaee say roknay wala had say barh janay wala gunehgaar
  68,13,Gardan kash phir sath hi beynasab ho
  68,14,Us ski sirkashi sirf iss liye hai kay who maal wala aur beton wala hai
  68,15,Jab uss kay samnay humari aayaten parhi jaati hain to keh deta hai kay yeh to aglon kay qissay hain
  68,16,Hum bhi us ski soond (naak) per daagh dengay
  68,17,Be-shak hum ney unhen issi tarah aazmaliya jiss tarah hum ney baagh walon ko aazmaya tha job unho ney qasman khayen kay subha hotay hi iss baagh kay phal utar lengay
  68,18,Aur inshaAllah na kaha
  68,19,Pus iss per teray rab ki janib say aik bala chaaron taraf ghoom gaee aur yeh so hi rahey thay
  68,20,Pus who baagh aisa hogaya jesay kati hui kheti
  68,21,Abb subha hotay hi unho ney aik doosray ko aawazen dea
  68,22,Kay agar tumhen phal utarnay hain to apni kheti per saweray hi saweray chal paro
  68,23,phir yeh sab chupkay chupkay yeh baten kertay huye chalay
  68,24,Kay aaj kay din koi miskeen tumharay pass na aanay paye
  68,25,Aur lapkay huye subha subha gaye (Samajh rahey thay) kay hum qaaboo paagaye
  68,26,job unho ney boogh dekha to kehnay logay yaqeenan hum raasta photo gaee
  68,27,Nahi nahi bulkay humari qismat phoot gaee
  68,28,Inn sab main jo behtar tha uss nay kaha kay mein tumsay na kehta tha kay tum Allah ki pakeezgi q iyon nahi biyan kertay
  68,29,To sab kehnay lagay humara rab pak hai be-shak hum hi zaalim thay
  68,30,Phir who aik doosray ki taraf rukh kerkay aapas mein malamat kernay lagay
  68,31,kehnay lagay haaye afsos! Yaqeenan hum sirkash thay
  68,32,Kiya ajab hai kay humara rab humen iss say behtar badla dey dey hum to abb apnay rab say hi aarzoo rakhtay hain
  68,33,Yun hi aafat aati hai aur aakhirat ki aafat both bari hai kaash! Unhen samajh hoti
  68,34,Perhezgaaron kay liye unkay rab kay pass nematon waali jannaten hain
  68,35,Kiya hum musalmanon ko misil gunehgaaron kay kerdengay
  68,36,Tumhen kiya hogaya kaisay foislay ker rahey ho
  68,37,Kiya tumharay pass koi kitab hai jiss mein tum parhtay ho
  68,38,Kay iss mein tumhari manmaani baten hon
  68,39,Yea tum nay hum say kuch qasman li hain ?jo qzayamat tak baaqi rahen kay tumharay liye who sab hai jot um apni taraf say muqarrar kerlo
  68,40,Inn say poochao to kay inn mein say kon iss baat ka zimeydaar (aur daaweydaar) hai
  68,41,Kiya inn kay koi shareek hain? To chahiye kay apnay apnay shareekor ko ley aayen agar yeh sachey hain
  68,42,Jiss din pindali khol di jayegi aur sajday kay liye bulaye jayengay to (sajdah) na ker saken gay
  68,43,Nigahen neechi hongi aur unn per zillat-o-khhuaari cha rahi hogi halankay yeh sajday kay liye (uss waqt bhi) bulaye jaatay thay jabkay sahih saalim thay
  68,44,Pus mujhay aur iss kalaam ko jhutlanay walay ko chor dey hum unhen iss tarah aahista aahista bhi na hoga
  68,45,Aur mein unhen dheel doonga be-shak meri tadbeer bari mazboot hai
  68,46,Kiya tu inn say koi ujrat chahta hai jiss kay tawaan say yeh dabay jatay hon
  68,47,Ya kiya inn kay pass ilm-e-ghaib hai jissay who likhtay hon
  68,48,Pus tu apnay rab kay hokum ka sabar say (intezar ker) aur machli walay ki tarah na ho jo jab kay uss nay ghum ki holat main dua ki
  68,49,Agar uss kay rab ki nemat na paaleti to yaqeenan who buray haalon main chatiyal medaan mein daal diya jata
  68,50,ussay uss kay rab nay phir nawaza aur ussay nak-kaaron main kerdiya
  68,51,Aur qareeb hai kay kafir apni tez nigahon say aap ko phusla den jab kabhi quran suntay hain aur keh detay hain yeh to zaroor deewana hai
  68,52,Darhaqeeqat yeh (quran) to tamam jahan walon kay liye sarasir naseehat hi hai
  69,1,Sabit honey wali
  69,2,Sabit honay wali kiya hay
  69,3,Aur tujhay kiya maloom kay wo sabit shuda kiya hay
  69,4,Is khrka deney wali ko samood aur aad ney jhutla dia tha
  69,5,(jis kay nateejay mein)samood to behad khufnak (aur onchi)awaz say halak ker diey gay
  69,6,Aur aad behad tez o tund hawa say gharat ker diey gaey
  69,7,Jis say in per lagatar sath rat aur aath din tak (Allah ney)musalat rakha.pus tum dekhtay kay yeh log zameen per istrah gir gaey jaisay kay khjoor kay khokhly tanay hon
  69,8,Kiya in mein say koi bhi tujhay baqi nazar araha hy
  69,9,Firoon aur iss say pehlay kay log aur jin ki bastiyan ulat di gaein unhon ney bhi khataein kiein
  69,10,Aur apney rab kay rasool ki nafarmani ki(bilakhir)Allah ney unhein(bhi)zaberdast girift mein ly lia
  69,11,jab pani mein tughyani agai to us waqat hum ney tumhein kashti mein charha liya
  69,12,Takay is say tumharay liey nasehat aur yad gar banadein aur(taky)yad rakhaney waly kan issy yad rakhein
  69,13,Pus jab kay soor mein ik phonk phonki jaey gi
  69,14,Aur zameen aur pahar utha liey jaein gay aur ik hi chot mein reza reza ker dey jaein gay
  69,15,Us din ho parnay wali(qiyamat)ho paray gi
  69,16,aur asman phat jaey ga aur us din bilkol boda ho jaey ga
  69,17,Is kay kinaron per farishtay hon gay aur tery perwardigar ka arsh us din aath(farishtay)apney opper uthaey hon gay
  69,18,Us din tum sab samney pesh kiey jao gay tumhara koi bhed poshida na rahy ga
  69,19,So jissay uska nama e amal us kay daein hath mein diya jaey ga to wo kehnay lagay ga kay lo mera nama e amal parh lo
  69,20,Mujhy to kamil yaqeen tha kay mujhy apna hisab milna hay
  69,21,Pus wo ik dil pasand zindagi mein ho ga
  69,22,Bulan o bala jant mein
  69,23,Jiss kay meway jhokay paray hon gay
  69,24,(in say kaha jaey ga) kay mazay say khao piyo apney in amal kay badlay jo tum ney guzishta zamanay mein kiy
  69,25,Lakin jissay uss(kay amal)ki kitab us kay baein hath mein di jaey gi wo to kahy ga kay kash kay mujhy meri kitab di hi na jati
  69,26,Aur mein janta hi na kay hisab kiya hay
  69,27,Kash ! kay moot (mera)kam hi tamam kerdyti
  69,28,Mery maal ney bhi mujhy kuch nafa na diya
  69,29,Mera ghalba bhi mujhsy jata raha
  69,30,(hokum hoga)issay pakar lo phir issy toq phyna do
  69,31,Phir isay dozakh mein dal do
  69,32,Phir issy asi zanjeer mein jiss ki paymaish satter hath ki hay jaker do
  69,33,Beshak yeh Allah azmat walay per iman na rakhta tha
  69,34,Aur miskeen kay khilanay per raghbat na dilata tha
  69,35,Pus aj iska na koi dost hay
  69,36,Aur na siway peep kay is ki koi ghiza hay
  69,37,Jissay ghunahgaron kay siwa koi nai kahey ga
  69,38,Pus mujhy qasam hay un chezon ki jinhein tum dekhtay ho
  69,39,Aur on chezon ki jinhein tum nahi dekhtay
  69,40,Kay be sahk yeh(quran)buzurgh rasool ka qool hay
  69,41,Yeh kisi shair ka qool nahi(afsos)tumhein bohat kam yaqeen hay
  69,42,Aur na kisi kahin ka qool hay(afsos)bohat kam nasehat lay rahay ho
  69,43,(ye to)rab ul alameen ka utara howa hay
  69,44,Aur ager yeh hum per koi bhi bat bana lyta
  69,45,To albata hum iska dahana hath paker letay
  69,46,Phir is ki sheyrag kaat detay
  69,47,Phir tum mein say koi bhi mujhy issy roknay wala na hota
  69,48,Yaqeenan yeh quran perhezgaron kay liye nasehat hay
  69,49,Humein pori tarah maloom hay kay tum mein say baaz iskay jhotlanay waly hein
  69,50,beshak (yeh jhutlan)kafiron per hasrat hay
  69,51,Aur beshak (o shuba)yeh yaqeni haq hay
  69,52,Pus to apney rab e azeem ki paki biyan ker
  70,1,Aik sawal kernay walay ney uss azab ka swal kiya jo wazeh honay wala hay
  70,2,Kafiron per jissay koi hatanay wala nahi
  70,3,Uss Allah ki taraf say jo seerhiyon wala hay
  70,4,Jiss ki taraf farishtay aur rooh charhtay hein aik din mein jiss ki miqdaar pachas hazar saal ki hay
  70,5,Pus to achi tarah sabar ker
  70,6,Beshak yeh uss (azab) ko door samajh rahe hein
  70,7,Hum issay qareeb hi dekhatay hein
  70,8,Jiss din aasman misil tel ki talchat kay hojayega
  70,9,Aur pohaar misil rangeen oon kay hojey gay
  70,10,Aur koi dost kissi dost ko na poochay ga
  70,11,(Halankay) aik doosray ko dikha diye jaeyen gay gunehgar uss din kay azab kay badlay fidye mein apney beton ko
  70,12,Apni biwi ko aur apney bhai ko
  70,13,Aur apney kunbay ko jo issay panah deta tha
  70,14,Aur roy e zameen kay sab logon ko dena chahyega takay yeh ussay nijat dilaye
  70,15,Mager hergiz yeh na hoga yaqeenan wo shoal wali (aag)hai
  70,16,Jo mun aur sar ki khal khench lynay wali hay
  70,17,Wo her us shaks ko pukaray gi jo pechay hata aur mun morta hay
  70,18,Aur jama ker kay samnbhal rakhta hay
  70,19,Beshak insan baray kachy dil wala banaya gaya hay
  70,20,Jab is say musibat puhanchti hay to har bara uthta hay
  70,21,aur jab rahat milti hay to bukhul kernay lagta hay
  70,22,Mager wo namazi
  70,23,J apnai namaz per hameshagi kernay walay hein
  70,24,Aur jin kay maalon mein mukarra hisa hay
  70,25,Mangnay walon ka bhi aur sawal say bachnay walon ka bhi
  70,26,Aur jo insaf kay din per yaqeen rakhtay hein
  70,27,Aur jo apney rab kay azab say dertay rehtay hein
  70,28,Beshak un kay rab ka azab bekhof honay ki chez nahi
  70,29,Aur jo log apni sharm gahon ki (haram say)hifazat kertay hein
  70,30,Han unki biwion aur londion kay bary mein jin kay wo malik hein.unhein koi malamat nahi
  70,31,Ab jo koi is kay ilawa(rah)dhonday ga to asay log had say guzar janay walay hongay
  70,32,Aur jo apni amanton ka aur apney qol o qarar ka pass rakhtay hein
  70,33,Aur jo apni gawahion per sidhay aur qaim rehtay hein
  70,34,Aur jo apni namazon ki hifazat kertay hein
  70,35,Yehi log janton mein izat walay hongay
  70,36,Pus kafoiron ko kia hogaya hay kay wo teri taraf dortay atay hein
  70,37,Daein aur baein say giroh kay giroh
  70,38,Kia in mein say her ik ki tawaqa yeh hay kay wo nematon wali janat mein dakhil kia jaey ga
  70,39,(aisa) hergiz nahi ho ga hum ney unhein is(chez) say paida kia hay jiss say wo jantay hein
  70,40,Pus mujhy qasam hay mashrikon aur maghribon kay rab ki (kay)hum yaqeenan qadir hein
  70,41,Is per kay in kay ewaz in say achay log lay ayein aur hum aajiz nahi hein
  70,42,Pus to inhein jagherta khelata chor day yahan ytak kay yeh apney us din say jamilein jis ka un say wada kia jata hay
  70,43,Jis din yeh qabron say dortay hoy niklein gay goya kay wo kisi jaga ki taraf tez tez jarahy hein
  70,44,In ki ankhein jhoki hoi hongi in per zilat charahi hon gi yeh hay wo din jis ka un say wada kia jata tha
  71,1,Yaqeenan hum ney Nooh(alh e salam)ko inki qom ki taraf bheja kay apni qom ko darado (aur khabaerdar kerdo) isss say pehlay kay inkay pass dardnak azab ajaye
  71,2,(Nooh alh e salam ney)kaha aey meri qom mein tumhein saaf saaf daranay wala hun
  71,3,Kay tum Allah ki ibadat kero aur issi say daro aur mera kaha maano
  71,4,To wo tumhary gunha bukhsh day ga aur tumhein aik waqat mukarrera tak chor dega YaqeenanAllah ka wada jab aajata hay to moakhir nahi hota kaash kay tumhien samjh hoti
  71,5,(nooh alh e salam ney) kaha aey mery perwardigar!mein ney apni qom ko raat din teri taraf bulaya hai
  71,6,Mager meray bulanay say yeh log aur ziyada bhagnay lagay
  71,7,Mein ney jab khabi unhein teri bakhsish kay liye bulaya unhon ney apni ungliyan apney kaano mein daal lein aur apney kapron ko orh liya aur urh gaye aur bara takabur kiya
  71,8,Phir mein ney unhein ba-awaz buland bulaya
  71,9,Aur beshak mein ney insay elaaniya bhi kaha aur chupkay chupkay bhi
  71,10,Aur mein ney kaha kay apney rab say apney gunha bakhswao(aur maafi mango)wo yaqeenan bara bakhsnay wala hay
  71,11,Wo tum per aasman ko khob barsata hua chor dega
  71,12,Aur tumhein khob pay dar pay maal aur olaad mein taraqi dega Aur tumhein baaghat dega aur tumharay liye nikaal dega
  71,13,Tumhein kiya hogaya hay kay tum Allah ki bartari ki aqeedah nahi rakhtay
  71,14,Halankay uss ney tumhein tarah tarah say paida kiya hay
  71,15,Kiya tum nahi dekhtay kay Allah Talah ney kiss tarah opper talay sath asman paida ker diey hein
  71,16,Aur in mien chand ko khob jagmata banaya hai aur sooraj ko roshan chiragh banaya hay
  71,17,Aur tum ko zameen say aik (khass ehtimam say)ugaya hai(aur paida kiya hai)
  71,18,Phir tumhein issi mein lota leya jaeyga aur(aik khass tareeqay)say phir nikalay ga
  71,19,Aur tumharay liye zameen ko Allah Taalaa ney farsh banadiya hay
  71,20,Takay tum uski kushada raahon mein chalo phiro
  71,21,Nooh(alh e salam) ney kaha aey meray perwardigar!in logon ney meri to nafarmani ki aur aison ki farmanbardari ki jinkay maal o olaad ney inko(yaqeenan)nuksan hi mein barhaya hai
  71,22,Aur in logon ney bara sakht fareeb kiya
  71,23,Aur kaha unhon ney kay hergiz apney maaboodon ko na chorna aur na wad aur suwaa aur yaghoos aur yaooq aur nasar ko(chorna)
  71,24,Aur unhon ney bohat say logon ko gumrah kiya (elaahi)tu in zaalimon ki gumrahi aur barha
  71,25,Yeh log ba sabab apney gunaahon kay dabo deygay aur jahanum mein phuncha diey gaye aur Allah kay siwa apna koi madadgar unhonay na paya
  71,26,Aur Nooh(alh e salam)ney kaha kay aey mery paalnay walay! To roy e zameen per kissi kafir ko rehnay sehnay wala na chor
  71,27,Ager to enhen chor dega to (yaqeenan)yeh tery (aur)bandon ko(bhi)gumrah kardeingay aur yeh faajiron aur dheet kafiron hi ko janum deingay
  71,28,Aey meray perwardigar!to mujhay aur meray maa baap aur jo eman ki halat mein meray ghar +mein aye aur tamam momin mardon aur auraton ko bakhsh dey aur kafiron ko siwaey barbadi key aur kissi baat mein na barha
  72,1,Aey Muhammad (P.B.U.H)) aap keh dein kay mujhy wahi ki gai hay kay jinno ki ik jamat ney (quran)suna or kaha kay hum ney ajeeb quarn suna hay
  72,2,Jo rah e rast ki tarf rahnumai kerta hay hum is per iman la chukay (ab)hum her giz kisi ko bhi apney rab ka sharek na banein gay
  72,3,Aur beshak hamary rab ki shan bari buland hay aur na us ney kisi ko (apni) biwi banaya hay aur na beta
  72,4,Aur yeh kay kehtay rahein hein hamary nadan logAllah kay bary mein bhat khilaf e haq batein
  72,5,Aur hum to yehi samjhtay rahy kay namumkin hay kay insan aur jinnat Allah per jhoti batein lagaein
  72,6,Baat yeh hay kay chand insan baaz jinnat say panah talab kertay thy jiss say jinnat apnai serkashi mein aur barh gay
  72,7,Aur (insano)ney bhi tum jino ki tarah guman ker liya tha kay Allah kisi ko na bhyjay ga(ye kisi ko dobara zinda an kery ga)
  72,8,Aur hum ney asman ko tatool ker dekha to ussy sakht chokidaron aur sakht sholon say pur paya
  72,9,Iss say pehlay hum baatein suneinkay liye asman mein jagah jagah beth jaya kertay thy .jo bhi kan lagata hay wo ik sholay ko apni taak mein pata hay
  72,10,Hum nahi jantay kay zameen walon kay sath kisi burai ka irada kiya gaya hay ya in kay rab ka irada in kay sath bhalai ka hay
  72,11,Aur yeh kay(beshak)baaz to hum mein nekokar hein aur baaz iskay barakas bhi hein hum mukhtalif tareeqon say batay hoy hein
  72,12,Aur hum ney samajh liya hay kay hum Allah Talah ko zameen mein hergiz aajiz nahi ker saktay aur na hum bhag ker issy hara saktay hein
  72,13,Hum to hidayat ki bat suntay hi is per eman la chukay aur jo bhi apney rab per eman laye ga us say na kisi nuksan ka andesha hay na zulm-o-sitam ka
  72,14,Han hum mein baaz to musalman hein baaz be-insaf hein pus jo farmaberdar hogay unhon ney to raah-e-raast ka qasad kiya
  72,15,Aur jo zalim hein wo jahanum ka endhen bangay
  72,16,Aur (aey Nabi yeh bhi khay do )kay log raaah e rast per seedhay rehtay to yaqeenan hum enhein both waffir pani pilatay
  72,17,Takay hum iss munhein azmalein aur jo sahks apney perwedigar kay zikar say mun pherlay ga to Allah Talah ussay sakht azab mein mubtila kerdayga
  72,18,Aur yeh kay mesjidein sirf Allah hi kay liye khass hein pus Allah Talah kay sath kissi aur ko na pukaro
  72,19,Aur jab Allah ka banda uss ki ibadat kay liye khara hoa to qareeb tha kay wo bheer ki bheer ban ker uss per pal paren
  72,20,Aap keh dijey kay mein to sirf apney rab hi ko pukarta hon aur iss kay sath kissi ko shareek nahi banata
  72,21,Keh dijey kay mujhy tumhary kissi nuksan nafa ka ikhtiyar nahi
  72,22,Kehdijey kay mujhy hergiz koi Allah say bacha nahi sakta aur mein hergiz uss kay siwa koi jay e panah bhi paa nahi sakta
  72,23,Albata (mera kam) Allah ki baat aur iss kay peghamaat(logon ko)phuncha dena hia(abb)jo bhi Allah aur uss kay rasool kin a maanay ga uss kay liye jahanum ki aag hai jiss mein aisay log hamesha rahengay
  72,24,(unki aankh na khulaygi)Yahan tak kay ussay dekhlen jiss ka unko wada diya jata hia pus unqareeb jaan lengay kay kiss ki jamat kum hai
  72,25,Kehdijey kay mujhy maloom nahi kay jiss ka wada tum say kiya jata hai wo qareeb hia ya mera rab uss kay liye door ki muddat mukarrer keryga
  72,26,Wo ghaib ka jannay wala hai aur apney ghaib per kisi ko mutlaa nahi kerta
  72,27,Siwaey uss peyghamber kay jissay wo pasand kerley lekin usskay bhi aagay pechay pehraydar muqarrer kerdyta hai
  72,28,Takay unkay apney rab kay paygham phoncha denay ka ilm hojaey.Allah talah ney unkay aas pass (ki tamam cheezon )ka ehaata ker rakha hai aur her cheez ki gintee ka shumaar ker rakha hai
  73,1,Aey kapray mein lipatnay walay
  73,2,Rat (kay waqat namaz) mein khary hojao mager kam
  73,3,Adhi rat ya is say bhi kuch kam kerly
  73,4,Ya is per barha dy aur quran ko thehar thehar kar (saf )parha ker
  73,5,Yaqeenan hum tuj per bohat bhari bat anqareeb nazil kerein gay
  73,6,Beshak rat ka uthna dil jamai kay liye intehai munasib hay aur bat ko bohat durust ker daynay wala hay
  73,7,Yaqeena tujhay din mein bohat shughal rahta hay
  73,8,To apney rab kay nam ka ziakr kiya ker aur tamam khalaiq say kat ker us ki taraf mutawajha ho ja
  73,9,Mashriq o maghrib ka perwardigar jis ka koi maabood nahi to usko apna karsaz bana lay
  73,10,Aur jo kuch wo kahy to sehta rah aur wazedari kay sath un say alag thalag rah
  73,11,Aur mujhy aur in jhotlanay waly asoda hal logon ko chor day aur inhein zara si muhlat dy
  73,12,Yaqeenan hamary han sakht biriyan hein aur sulagti haoi jahanum hay
  73,13,Aur halq mein atakney wala khana hay aur dard deney wal azb
  73,14,Jiss din zamen aur pahar thar thara jaein gzy aur phaar missal bhor bhori rait kay telon kay hojaein gay
  73,15,Beshak hum ney tumhari taraf bhi tum per gawahi dynay wala rasool bhyj diya hay jaisa kay hum ney firoon kay pass rasol bhyja tha
  73,16,To firoon ney us rasol kin a frmani ki to hum ney usy sakht (wabal ki)pakar mein paker liya
  73,17,Tum ager kafir rahy to usdin kaisy panah pao gay jo din bachon ko burha ker day ga
  73,18,Jiss dion asman phat jaey ga Allh Talah ka yeh wada ho ker hi rahnay wala hay
  73,19,Beshak yeh nasehat hay pus jo chahey apney rab ki taraf rah ikhtiyar keray
  73,20,Apka rab bakhobi janta hay ka yap aur aap kay sath kay logon ki ik jamat qareeb do tahai rat kay aur adhi rat kay aur ik tahai rat kay tahajud parhti hay aur rat din ka pora andaza Allah Talaa ko hi hay.wo (khob) janta hay kay tum is say hergiz na nibha sako gay pus isnay tum per meharbani ki lyhaza jitna qyran parhna tumhary liye asan ho itna hi parho wo janta hay kay tum mein baaz bimar bhi hongay baaz dosray zameen mein chal phir ker Allah Talah ka fazal (yani rozi bhi)talash kerein gay aur kuch log Allah talah ki rah mein jahad bhi kerein gay so tum basani jitna quran parh sako parho aur namaz ki pabandi rakho. Aur zakat dytay raha kero aur Allah Talah ko acha qarz do aur jo neki tum apney liye agay bhyjo gay ussy Allah talah kay han bhyter say bhyter aur sawab mein bohat ziyada pao gay ALLAH TALAH say moafi mangtay raho yaqeenan AllahTalah bakhshney wala meharban hy
  74,1,Aey kapra orhnay waly
  74,2,Khara ho ja aur agah ker day
  74,3,Aur apney rab hi ki baraiyan biyan ker
  74,4,Apney kapron ko pak rakha ker
  74,5,Na paki ko chor day
  74,6,Aur ahsan ker kay ziyada lynay ki khuwaish na ker
  74,7,Aur apney rab ki rah mein sabar ker
  74,8,Pus jab kay sor mein phonk mari jaey gi
  74,9,To wo din bara sakht din hoga
  74,10,(jo) Kafiron per asan na hoga
  74,11,Mujhy aur usay chor day jissy mein ney akela paida kiya hay
  74,12,Aur issy bohat sa maal dy rakha hay
  74,13,Aur hazir bash ferzand bhi
  74,14,Aur mein ney ussy bohat kushadigi dy rakhi hay
  74,15,Phir bhi uski chahat hay kay mein usy or ziyada don
  74,16,Nahi nahi wo hamari ayaton ka mukhalif hy
  74,17,an qareeb mein usy ik sakht charhai charhaon ga
  74,18,Us ney ghor ker kay tajweez ki
  74,19,Usy halakat ho kaisi(tajweez)sochi
  74,20,Wo phir gharat ho kis tarah andaza kiya
  74,21,Us ney phir dekha
  74,22,Phir teweri char hai or mun banaya
  74,23,Phir pechay hat gaya aur ghoroor kiya
  74,24,Aur khynay laga yeh to sirf jado hay jo naqal kiya jata hay
  74,25,Siwaey insani kalam kay kuch bhi nahi
  74,26,Mein anqareeb usy dfozakh mein dalon ga
  74,27,aur tujhay kiya khaber kay dozakh kiya chez hay
  74,28,Na wo baqi rakhti hay aur na chorti hay
  74,29,Khal ko jholsa dyti hay
  74,30,Aur is mein unnees(19)(farshtay mukarrar) hein
  74,31,Hum ney dozakh kay daroghy say farishtay rakhein hein aur hum ney unki tadad sirf kafiron ki azmaish kay liye mukarrar ki hay takay ahl e kitab yaqeen ker lein.aur ahl e eman kay eman mein asafa ho jay aur ahl e kitab aur ahl e eman shak na kerien aur jin kay dilon mein bimari hay wo aur kafir kahein kay is biyan say Allah Talah jissy chata hay ghumrah kerta hay aur jissy chata hay hidayat dyta hay tery rab kay lashkaron ko us kay siwa koi nahi janta yeh to kul bani adam kay liye sar a sar pind o nasehat hay
  74,32,Sach khyta hon qasam hay chand ki
  74,33,Aur rat ki jab wo pechay hatay
  74,34,Aur subha ki jab kay roshan hojaey
  74,35,Kay (yaqeenan wo jahanum)bari chezon mein say ik hay
  74,36,Bani adam ko daraney wali
  74,37,(yani)ussayn jo tum mein say agay barhna chaey ya pechay hanta chaey
  74,38,Her shaks apney amal kay badlay mein girwi hay
  74,39,Magar daein hath walay
  74,40,Kay wo baheshton mein (bethay hoy)gunehgaron say
  74,41,Sawal kertay hongay
  74,42,Tumhein dozakh mein kis chez ney dala
  74,43,Wo jawab deingay kay hum namazi na thy
  74,44,Na miskeeno ko khana khilatay thy
  74,45,Aur hum bhas kernay waly(inkarion )ka sath dy ker bhas mubahisa mein mashghol raha kertay thy
  74,46,Aur roz e jaza ko jhutlatay thy
  74,47,Yahan tak kay humein mot agai
  74,48,Pus inhein sifarish kernay walon ki sifarish nafa na dy gi
  74,49,Inhein kiya hogaya hay?kay nasehat say mun mor rahy hein
  74,50,Goya kay wo bidkay hoy gadhay hein
  74,51,Jo sher say bhagaein hon
  74,52,Balkay in mein say her shaks chata hay kay usay kholi hoi kitabein di jaein
  74,53,Hergiz asa nahi (hosakta balkay)yeh qiyamat say bay khof hein
  74,54,sachi bat to yeh hay kay yeh(quran)ik nasehat hay
  74,55,Ab jo chahey issy nasehat hasil kery
  74,56,Aur wo us waqat nasehat hasil kerein gay jab Allah Talah chahein wo issi laiq hein kay issy darein aur iss laiq bhi kay wo bakhshy
  75,1,Mein qasam khata hun qayamat kay din ki
  75,2,Aur qasam khata hun uss nafas ki jo malamat kernay wala ho
  75,3,Kiya insan yeh khayal kert hai kay hum uss ki hadiyan jama kerengay hi nahi
  75,4,Han zaror kerengay hum to qadir hain kay usski por por tak durust kerdein
  75,5,Bulkay insan to chahta hai kay aagay aagay na farmaniyan kerta jaey
  75,6,Poochata hai kay qayamat ka din kab aaye ga
  75,7,Pus jiss waqat kay nigha pathra jaeygi
  75,8,Aur chand benoor hojaey ga
  75,9,Aur soraj aur chand jama kerdiye jaeingay
  75,10,Uss din insan kahega kay aaj bhegnay ki jagah kahan hai
  75,11,Nahi nahi koi panahgah nahi
  75,12,Aaj to teray perwardigar ki tarf hi qarar gah hai
  75,13,Aaj insan ko uss kay aagay bhejay huye aur peechay choray hoye say aagah kiya jaeyga
  75,14,Bulkay insan khud apney upper aap hujjat hai
  75,15,Agercha kitnay hi bahanay pesh keryga
  75,16,(ay nabi) aap quran ko jadi (yaad kernay)kay liey apni zabaan ko herkat na den
  75,17,Iss ka jama kerna aur (aap ki zaba say)perhna humaray zimmay hai
  75,18,Hum jab issay parhlen to aap iss kay parhnay ki perwi kerein
  75,19,Phir is ka wazeh ker dyna hamary zimy hay
  75,20,Nahi nahi tum jaldi milnay wali(duniya) ki mohabat rakhtay ho
  75,21,Aur akhrat ko chor bethy ho
  75,22,Uss roz bohat say chehery ter o taza aur ba runaq hongay
  75,23,Apney rab ki taraf dekhtay hongay
  75,24,Aur kitnay chehry us din (bad ronaq aur) udas hongay
  75,25,Samjhtay hongay kay in kay sath kamar toor dynay wala mamla ki jaey ga
  75,26,Nahi nahi jab roz hansli tak phunchay gi
  75,27,Aur kaha jaeyga koi char phonk kernay wala hay
  75,28,Aur jan liya unsay kay yeh waqat judai hay
  75,29,Aur pindli say pindli lipat jaey gi
  75,30,Aj tery perwardigar ki taraf chalna hay
  75,31,Us ney na to tasdeeq ki aur na namaz ada ki
  75,32,Bulkay jhutlaya aur roh gatdani ki
  75,33,Phir apney gher walon kay pass itrata hoya gaya
  75,34,Afsos hay tujhay per hasrat hay tujh per
  75,35,Waaye hai aur kharabi hay tery liye
  75,36,Kiya insan yeh samjhta hay kay usy be kaar chor diay jaey ga
  75,37,Kiya wo iki ghary pani ka katra na tha jo tapkaya gaya tha
  75,38,Phir wo laho ka lothra hogay phir Allah ney usy paida kia aur durasat bana diya
  75,39,Phir us say joray yani nar o mada banay
  75,40,kiya (Allah Talah) iss (amar)per qadir nahi kay murday ko zinda kerday
  76,1,Yaqeenan guzra hai insan per ik waqat zamanay mein jab kay yeh koi qabe e zikar chez na tha
  76,2,Besahak hum ney insan ko milay julay nutfay say imtehan kay liye paida kiya aur uss ko sunta dekhta banaya
  76,3,Hum ney ussay raah dikhai abb khua wo shukar guzar banay khua na shukra
  76,4,Yaqeenaa hum ney kafiron kay liye zanjeeron aur toq aur sholon wali aag tayar ker rakhi hay
  76,5,Besahk neek log wo jam piyein gay jiss ki azmaish kafiron ki hay
  76,6,Jo aik chesma hai jiss say Allah kay banday piyen gay uss ki nehrein nikaal ley jaengay (jidher chahen)
  76,7,Jo nazar poori kertay hein aur uss din say dartay hein jiss ki buraee charon taraf phel jaanay wali hia
  76,8,Aur Allah Taalaa ki mohabat mein khana khilatay hein miskeen yateem aur qediyon ko
  76,9,Hum to tumhein sirf Allah Taalaa ki raza mandi kay liye khilatay hein na tum say badla chatay hein na shuker guzari
  76,10,Beshak hum apney perwardigar say uss din ka khof kertay hein jo udaasi aur sakhti wala hoga
  76,11,Pus inhen Allah Taala ney uss din ki buraee say bacha liya aur inhen taazgi aur khushi phonchaee
  76,12,Aut inhen inkay sabar kay badlay jannat aur reshmi libass ata farmaye
  76,13,Yeh wahan takhton per takiey lagaey huye bethen gay na wahan aftab ki garmi dfekhein gay ja jaray ki sakhti
  76,14,In jannaton kay saaye un per jhukey huye hongay aur inkay (meway aur)gunchay neechay latkaaey huye hongay
  76,15,Aur in per chandi kay bartano aur in jaamon ka dor keraya jayega jo sheeshay kay hongay
  76,16,Sheeshy bhi chandi kay jinko(saqi ney)andazay say nap rakha hoga
  76,17,Aur inhein wahan wo jam pilaya jaey ga jin ki amezish zanjabeel ki hogi
  76,18,Jaanat ki ik nehar say jiss ka nam salsabeel hay
  76,19,Aur inkay ird gird ghoomtey phirtay hongay wo kumsin bachay jo hamesha rehnay walay hein jab tu unhein dekhay to samjhay key wo bikhray hoey sachay moti hein
  76,20,Tu wahan jahan kahin bhi nazar daley ga saraser nematein aur azeem-ul-shan saltanat hi dekhay ga
  76,21,In kay jismoon per sabz bareek aur motay reshmi kapray hongay aur enhen chandi kay kangan ka zewar pehnaya jaeyga aur inhein unka rab pak saaf sharab pilaey ga
  76,22,(kaha jaeyga)kay yeh hai teray aemal ka badla aur tumhari koshish kiqadar ki gaee
  76,23,Beshak hum ney tujh per ba tedreej quran nazil kiya hai
  76,24,Pus to apney rab kay hokum per qaim rah aur in mein say kissi gunhagar ya na shukray ka kaha na maan
  76,25,Aur apney rab kay naam ka subha o sham zikar kiya ker
  76,26,Aur raat kay waqat uss kay saamnay sajday ker aur bohat raat tak uss ki tasbeeh kiya ker
  76,27,Behak yeh log jaldi milnay wali(duniya) ko chahtay hein aur apney peechay aik baray bhari din ko choray detay hein
  76,28,Hum ney inhein peda kiya aur hum ney hi in key jor aur bandhan mazboot kiey aur hum jab chahen in kay ewaz in jesay auron ko badal layen
  76,29,Yaqeenan yeh to aik naseehat hai pus jo chahey apney rab ki raah lelay
  76,30,Aur tum na chahogay magar yeh kay Allah Taalaa hi chahey beshak Allah Talah ilm wala ba hikmat hai
  76,31,Jissay chahey apni rehmat mein daakhil kerley aur zaalimon kay liye uss ney dard naak azab tayyar ker rakha hai
  77,1,Dil khush kun chalti hawaon ki qasam
  77,2,Phir zor say jhonka denay walion ki qasam
  77,3,Phir(abar ko) ubhaar ker peraganda kernay waliyon ki qasam
  77,4,Phir haq o batil ko joda joda kerdenay walay
  77,5,Aur wahee laanay walay farishton ki qasam
  77,6,Jo (wahee) ilzaam utarnay ya aggah kerdenay kay liey hoti hai
  77,7,Jiss cheez ka tum saywada kiya jata hai wo yaqeenan honay wali hai
  77,8,Pus jab sitary be nor kerdiey jaeingay
  77,9,Aur jab aasman tor phor diya jaey ga
  77,10,Aur jab pahar tukray tukray kerdkay ura diya jaeyga
  77,11,Aur jab rasoolon ko waqat muqarrara per laya jaeyga
  77,12,Kiss din kay liey (in sab ko)mo akkhir kiya gaya hai
  77,13,Faislay kay din kay liey
  77,14,Aur tujhay kiya maloom kay faislay ka din kiya hai
  77,15,Uss din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,16,Kiya hum ney aglon ko halak nahi kiya
  77,17,Phir hum inkay baad peechlon ko laey
  77,18,Hum gunehgaron kay sath issi tarah kertay hein
  77,19,Uss din jhutlanay walon kay liey wail(afsos) hai
  77,20,Kiya hum ney tumhein haqeer paani say(money say) peda nahi kiya
  77,21,Phir hum ney ussay mazboot o mehfooz jaga mein rakha
  77,22,Aik muqarrara waqat tak
  77,23,Phir hum ney andaza kiya aur hum kiya khoob andaza kernay walay hein
  77,24,Uss din takzeeb kernay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,25,KIya hum ney zameen ko sametnay wali nahi banaya
  77,26,Zindon ko bhi aur murdon ko bhi
  77,27,Aur hum ney iss mein buland o bhar pahar bana diey aur tum hein seraab kernay wala meetha paani pilaya
  77,28,Uss din jhoot jannay walon kay liey waaye aur afsos hai
  77,29,Uss dozakh ki taraf jao jissay tum jhutlatay rahey thay
  77,30,Chalo teen shakhon waly saaye ki taraf
  77,31,Jo dar asel na saaye denay wala hai aur na sholay say bacha sakhta hai
  77,32,yaqeenan dozakh chingariyan phenkti hai jo misil mehal kay hein
  77,33,Goya kay who zard unt hain
  77,34,Aaj in jhot jannay walon ki durgat hai
  77,35,Aaj (ka din)wo din hai yeh bol bhi na sakein gay
  77,36,Na unhen maazrat ki ijazat di jaeygi
  77,37,Uss din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,38,Yeh hai faislay ka din hum ney tumhein aur aglon ko sab ko jama kerliya hai
  77,39,Pus agar tum mujh say koi chaal chal saktay hoto chal lo
  77,40,Waaye hai uss din jhutlanay walon kay liey
  77,41,Beshak perhezgar log sayon mein hein aur meethay chashmon mein
  77,42,Aur unn mewon mein jin ki wo khawaish kerein
  77,43,(aey jannatiyon!)khao piyo mazay say apney kiey huey aamal kay badley
  77,44,Yaqeenan hum neki kernay walon o iss tarah jaza detay hein
  77,45,Uss din sacha na jannay walon kay liye wail(afsos) hai
  77,46,(aey jhutlanay walon tum duniya mein)thora sa khaloo aur faeeda uthalo beshak tum gunehgar ho
  77,47,Uss din jhutlanay walon kay liye sakht halakat hai
  77,48,In say jab kaha jata hai kay rukoo kerlo to nahi kertay
  77,49,Uss din jhutlanay walon ki tabbahi hai
  77,50,Abb iss quran kay baad kiss baat per eman layengay
  78,1,Yeh log kis chez kay bary mein poch gach ker rahy hein
  78,2,Us bari khabar kay mutaliq
  78,3,Jiss kay bary mein yeh ikhtylaf ker rahay hein
  78,4,Yaqenan yeh abhi jan lein gay
  78,5,Phir bil yaqeen inhein buhat jald maloom hojaey ga
  78,6,kiya hum nay zameen ko farsh nahi banaya
  78,7,Aur paharon ko mikhein(nahi banaya)
  78,8,Aur hum nay tumhein jora jora paida kiya
  78,9,Aur hum nay tumhari nend ko aram ka sabab banaya
  78,10,Aur rat ko hum nay parda banaya hay
  78,11,Aur din ko hum nay waqat e rozgar banaya
  78,12,Aur tumhary opper hum nay 7 masboot asman banaey
  78,13,Aur ik chamkta howa roshan chiragh(soraj)paida kiya
  78,14,Aur badlon say hum nay bakasrat bhyta hoa pani barsaya
  78,15,Atky us say anaj or sabza ugaein
  78,16,Aur ghanay bagh(bhi ugay)
  78,17,be-shak faislay kay din ka waqat mukarer hay
  78,18,Jiss din kay sor mein phonka jaey ga phir tum foj der foj chaly ao gay
  78,19,Aur asman khol diaya jaey ga to is mein darwazy darwazy hojaein gay
  78,20,Aur pahar chaly jaein gay pus wo sarab hojaein gay
  78,21,Be-shak dozakh ghat mein hay
  78,22,sarkashon ka thikana wohi hay
  78,23,Is mein wo mudaton tak pary rahein gay
  78,24,Na kabhi is mein khunki ka maza chakein gay na pani ka
  78,25,Siwaey garm pani aur(beyti)peep kay
  78,26,(Unko)pora pora badla milay ga
  78,27,Unhein to hisab ki tawaqa hi na thi
  78,28,Aur bebaki say hamari ayton ki takzeb kerty thy
  78,29,Hum nay her ik chez ko likh ker shumar ker rakah hay
  78,30,Ab tum(apnay kiey ka )maza chako hum tumhara azab bhi barhaty rahein gay
  78,31,Yaqeenan perhezgar logon kay liey kamyabi hay
  78,32,Baghat hein or angoor hay
  78,33,Aur nojawan kunwari hum omer auratein hein
  78,34,Aur chalkty hoy jam sharab hein
  78,35,Wahan na to who byhoda batein sunein gay aur na jhoti batein sunein gay
  78,36,(Unko) tery rab ki taraf say (unkay nek amal ka)yeh badla milay ga jo kafi inam hoga
  78,37,(Is rab ki taraf say milay ga jo kay)asmano ka aur zameen ka aur jo kuch in kay dermiyan hay inka perwardigar hay aur bari bakhsish kernay wala hay kisi ko is say bat chet kerney ka ikhtyar nahi hoga
  78,38,Jiss din roh or faristy safein bandh ker khary hongay to koi kalam na kersakay ga magar jis say rehman ijazat dayday aur wo thek bat zaban say nikalay
  78,39,Yeh din haq hay ab jo chaeiy apnay rab kay pass (nek amal kerkay) thikana banalein
  78,40,Hum nay tumhein unqareeb anay walay azab say dara diya(aur chokanna ker diya) hai. jis din insan apnay haton ki kamai ko dekh ly gaur kafir kahy ga kay kash!mein mitti hojata
  79,1,Doob ker sakhti say khenchnay walon ki qasam
  79,2,Band khol ker chora dyney walon ki qasam
  79,3,Aur terney phirnay walon ki qasam
  79,4,Phir dor ker agy barhnay walon ki qasam
  79,5,Phir kam ki tadbeer kernay walon ki qasam
  79,6,Jis din kanpney wali kanpe gi
  79,7,Us ky bad ik peechy aney wali (peechy peechy) aye gi
  79,8,(buhat se)dil us din dharakty hongy
  79,9,Gin ki nigahen nichi hongien
  79,10,kehty hein ke kiya hum pehli ki si halat ki taraf phir lot aye jaein gay
  79,11,Kiya us waqt jab ke hum bosida hadiyaan hojaein gay
  79,12,Kehty hein ke phir to ye lotna nuksandeh hay
  79,13,(maloom hona chaiey)wo to sirf ik (khufnak)dant hay
  79,14,Kay (jis kay zihar hoty hi )wo ik dam medan mein jama hojaein gay
  79,15,Kiya Musa (aleh e salam)ki khabar tumhein phunchi hay
  79,16,Jabkay unhein unkay rab nay pak medan TUA mein pukara
  79,17,(kay)tum firoon kay pass jao unsay sirkashi ikhtyar kerli hay
  79,18,ussy kaho kay kiya to apnai durstagi or islah chata hy
  79,19,Aur yeh ky mein tujhhy terey Rab ki rah dikhata takay tu (uss say) darnay lagy
  79,20,Pus ussay bari nishani dikhai
  79,21,To us ney jhutlaya aur na fermani ki
  79,22,Phir palta dor dhoop kertay huye
  79,23,Phir sabb ko jama kerty pukaara
  79,24,Tum sab ka rab mein hi hun
  79,25,To(sab say buland o baala)) Allah ney bhi usay aakhrat ky aur duneya ky azab mein giriftaar kerliya
  79,26,Be-shak is mein is shaks kay liye ibrat hy jo daray
  79,27,Kiya tumhara peda kerna zadadushwar hy ya aasman ka
  79,28,Iss ki bulandi unchi ki phir issay theek thak kerdia
  79,29,Is ski raat ko tareek banaya aur iss kay din ko nikala
  79,30,Aur is kay baad zameen ko (humwaar)bicha diya
  79,31,Iss mein say paani aur chaara nikala
  79,32,Aur paharon ko (mazboot) ghar diya
  79,33,Yeh sab tumhary aur tumhary janwaron kay fiady kat liey (hein)
  79,34,Aur jab wo bari afat(qiyamat) ayegi
  79,35,Jiss din kay insan apnay kiey hoy kamon ko yad kery ga
  79,36,Aur (her)dekhney waly kay samaney jahanum zahir ki jaey gi
  79,37,To jiss(shaks) nay sarkashi ki (hogi)
  79,38,Aur duneyawi zindagi ko tarjeeh di(hogi)
  79,39,(uska)thikana jahanum hi hay
  79,40,Han jo shaks apnay rab kay samaney khara honay say darta raha hogaaur apnay nafas ko khuwahish say roka hoga
  79,41,To uska thikana janat hi hay
  79,42,Log ap say qiyamat kay waqay honay ka waqat daryafat kerty hein
  79,43,Ap ko is kay biyan kernay say kiaya taaluq
  79,44,Isskay ilam ki inteha to Allah ki janib hay
  79,45,Ap to sirf issy derty rahney walon ko agha kernay walay hein
  79,46,Jis roz ye ussay dekh lein gay to asa malom hoga kay sirf din ka akhiri hisa ya awal hisa hi(duniya mein)rahy hein
  80,1,Wo turush ro howa aur mon mor lia
  80,2,(sirf isliey)kay uskay pass ik nabina aya
  80,3,Tujhy kia khabar shayad wo sanwar jata
  80,4,Ya nasehat sunta or usy nesehat fiada phunchati
  80,5,Jo be parwaii kerta hay
  80,6,Uski taraf to pori twaja kerta hy
  80,7,halankay us kay na sanwarney say tujh per koi ilzam nahi
  80,8,Aur jo shaks tery pass dorta hoywa ata hay
  80,9,Aur wo der (bhi) raha hay
  80,10,To us say byrukhi barta hay
  80,11,Yeh thek nahi quran is nasehat (ki chez) hay
  80,12,jo chahy ussy nasehat ly
  80,13,(ye to)purazmat sahifon mein hay
  80,14,Jo buland o bala or pak saf hein
  80,15,Asy likhney walon kay haton mein hy
  80,16,Jo buzurgh or pakbaz hein
  80,17,Allah ki mar insan per kaisa nashukra hay
  80,18,Ussy Allah nay kis chez say paida kiya
  80,19,Ussy ik nutfay say phir andazy per rakha ussko
  80,20,Phir us kay liey rasta asan kiya
  80,21,Phir usy mot di aur phir qabar mein dafan kiya
  80,22,Phir jab chaey ga zinda ker day ga
  80,23,Hergiz nahi unsay ab tak Allah kay hokum ki byja awari nahi ki
  80,24,Insan ko chahye kay apnay khaney ko dekhy
  80,25,Kay hum nay khob pani barsaya
  80,26,Phir phara zamen ko achi tarah
  80,27,Phir is mein anaj ugaey
  80,28,Or angoor or tarkari
  80,29,Aur zeitoon or khajoor
  80,30,Aur gunjan baghat
  80,31,Aur mywa(aur ghass)chara(bhi ugaya)
  80,32,Tumhary istamal o faidy kay liey or tumhary chopayon kay liey
  80,33,Pus jab kay kan bhyray ker dyney wali (qiyamat)ajaey gi
  80,34,Us din admi apnay bhai say
  80,35,Aur apni maa or bap say
  80,36,Aur apni biwi or apni ulad say bhagy ga
  80,37,in mein say her ik ko us din asi fikar(damengeer)hogi jo uskay liey kafi hogi
  80,38,Us din bohat say chehry roshan hongy
  80,39,Jo hansty hoy aur hashshash bashshash hongay
  80,40,Aur baht say chehry usdin ghubar alod hon gay
  80,41,Jis per siyahi charhi hoi hogi
  80,42,wo yehi kafir badkirdar log hon gay
  81,1,Jab sooraj lappet liya jaey ga
  81,2,Aur jab sitary by noor hojaein gay
  81,3,Aur jab pahar chalaye jaein gya
  81,4,Aur jab das mah ki hamla oontniyan chor di jaein gi
  81,5,Aur jab wehshi janwar ikhattay kiey jaein gay
  81,6,Aur jab samander bharka diey jaien gay
  81,7,Aur jab janein (jimson say) mila dein jaein gein
  81,8,Aur jab zinda gari hoi larki say sawal kiya jaey ga
  81,9,Kay kis gunha ki waja say wo qatal ki gae
  81,10,Aur jab nama amal khol diey jaein gay
  81,11,Aur jab asman ki khal utar li jaey gai
  81,12,Aur jab jahanum bharkai jaei gi
  81,13,Aur jab jant nazdek kerdi jaey gi
  81,14,To us din her shaks jan lyga jo kuch yeh ker aya hoga
  81,15,Mein qasam khata hon pechay hatnay waly
  81,16,Chalnay phirney waly chupney waly sitaron ki
  81,17,Aur rat ki jab janey lagy
  81,18,Aur subha ki jab chamek ney lagy
  81,19,Yaqenan yeh ik buzrug rasool ka kaha howa hay
  81,20,Jo qooat wala hay arsh waly (Allah) kay nazdek buland martaba hay
  81,21,Jis ki (asmanon mein)ita-at ki jati hay amen hy
  81,22,Aur tumhara sathi dewana nahi hay
  81,23,isnay us(farishty)ko asman kay kholy kinary per dekha bhi hay
  81,24,Aur yeh ghaib ki baton ko batlaney mein bakhil bhi nahi
  81,25,Aur yeh quran shytan mardod ka kalam nahi
  81,26,Phir tum kahan jarahy ho
  81,27,Yeh to tamam jahan walon kay liey nasehat nama hay
  81,28,(bilkhosos)us kay liey jo tum mein say sedhi rah per chalna chahy
  81,29,Aur tum baghair parwardigar e alam kay chahaye kuch nahi chah saktay
  82,1,jab asman phat jaey ga
  82,2,Aur jab sitary jhar jaein gay
  82,3,Aur jab samander bhy niklein gay
  82,4,Aur jab qabreen (shak kerky) ukhar di jaey gi
  82,5,(us waqat)her shaks apnay agy bhyjy hoy aur pechay chory hoy(yani agly pechly amal)ko maloom ker lyga
  82,6,Ay insan tujhy apnay rab e karim say kis chez nay bhykaya
  82,7,Jis(rab nay)tujhy paida kiya phir thek thak kiya phir (durust)baraber banaya
  82,8,Jis sorat mein chaha tujhy jor diya
  82,9,Hergiz nahi balky tum to jaza o saza kay din ko jhotlaty ho
  82,10,Yaqenan tum per nigheban izat waly
  82,11,Likhney waly muqerer hein
  82,12,Jo kuch tum kerty ho wo janty hein
  82,13,Yaqenan nek log(jant kay assh o aram aur)nematon mein hongay
  82,14,Aur yaqenan bad kar log dozakh mein hongy
  82,15,Badly waly din is mein jaein agy
  82,16,Wo is say kabhi ghaib na honey paein gay
  82,17,Tujhy kuch khabar bhi hay kay badlay ka din kiya hay
  82,18,Mein tujhy phir (khyta hun kay )tujhay kiya maloom kay jaza (aur saza) ka din kiya hay
  82,19,Wo hay jis din koi shaks kisi shaks kay liye kissi cheez ka mukhtar na hoga aur (tamam ter) ehkaam us roz Allah kay hi hongay
  83,1,Bari kharabi hay nap tool mein kami kerney walon ki
  83,2,kay jab logon say nap kerlyty hein to pora pora lyty hein
  83,3,Aur jab inhein nap ker ya tool ker dyty hein to kam dyty hein
  83,4,kiya inhen apney marney kay bad ji uthney ka khayal nahi
  83,5,us azeem din kay liey
  83,6,Jis din sab log rab ul alameen kay samnay khary hongy
  83,7,yaqenan badkaron ka nama e amal sijeen mein hay
  83,8,Tujhy kiya maloom sijeen kiya hay
  83,9,(yeh to)LIkhi hoi kitab hay
  83,10,Us din jhotlaney walon ki bari khrabi hay
  83,11,Jo jaza o saza kay din ko jhotlaty hein
  83,12,Issy sirf wohi jhotlata hay jo had say agy nikal janey wala(aur) ghunaghar hota hay
  83,13,Jab iskay samnay hamari ayatein parhi jati hein to keh dyta hay kay yeh aglon kay afsaney hein
  83,14,Yun nahi balky in kay dilon per in kay amal ki waja say zang (charh gaya)hai
  83,15,Hergiz nahi yeh log us din apnay rab say oat mein rakhy jaein gay
  83,16,Phir yeh log bil yaqen jahanum mein jhonky jaein gay
  83,17,Phir keh diya jaey ga kay yehi hay wo jissy tum jhotlaty rahy
  83,18,Yaqenan yaqenan nekokaron ka nam e amal illieen mein hay
  83,19,Tujhy kiya pata kay illieen kiya hay
  83,20,(wo to) likhi hoi kitab hay
  83,21,Muqarab (farishty)iska mushahida kerty hein
  83,22,Yaqeena nek log (bari)nematon mein hongy
  83,23,Mesherion per bethy dekh rahy hongy
  83,24,To in kay chehron say hi nematon ki taro tazgi phychan lay ga
  83,25,Yeh log sir ba mehar khalis sharab pilaey jaeingy
  83,26,Jiss per mushk ki muhar hogi sabqat lay jeney walon ko isi mein sabqat kerni chahiey
  83,27,Aur isi ki amyzish tasneem ki hogi
  83,28,(Yani) wo chashma jis ka pani muqarab log piyein gay
  83,29,Gunha gar log iman walon ki hansi uraya kerty thy
  83,30,Aur in kay pass say guzarty hoy apas mein ankh kay isahry kerty thy
  83,31,Aur jab apnay walon ki taraf lot ty to dil lageyan kerty thy
  83,32,Aur jab inhein dekhty to kehty yaqeenan yeh log ghumrah(berah) hein
  83,33,Yeh in per pasban bana ker to nahi bhyjy gay
  83,34,Pus aj iman waly in kafiron per hansein gay
  83,35,Takhaton per bethy dekh rahy hongy
  83,36,Kay abb in munkiron nay jaisa yeh kerty thay poora poora badla pa liya
  84,1,Jab asman phat jaey ga
  84,2,Aur apney rab kay hokum per kan lagaey ga aur issi kay laiq wo hay
  84,3,Aur jab zameen (khench ker)phela di jaey gi
  84,4,Aur iss mein jo hai ussay wo ugal degi aur khali hojaigi
  84,5,Aur apney rab ky hokoom per kaan lagaye gi aur isi kay laeeq wo hy
  84,6,Aey insaan! Tu apney rab say milney tak yeh koshish aur tamam kaam aur mehnatein kerky ussymulaqatkerney wala hy
  84,7,To(us waqt) jis shaks kydahaney hath mein aamaal naama diya jaiyga
  84,8,Us ka hisab to bari aasani say liya jaey ga
  84,9,Aur wo apney ehal ki taraf hansi khushi lot ayega
  84,10,Han jis shaks ka aamaal nama us ki peeth ky peechy say diya jaey ga
  84,11,To wo maut ko bulaney lagyga
  84,12,Aur bharakti hui jahanum meindakhil hoga
  84,13,Yeh sahks apnay mutalqeen mein(duniya mein)khush tah
  84,14,Isska khayal tah kay Allah ki taraf loot ker hi na jaey ga
  84,15,Que nahi hanlankay iska rab usy bakhobi dekh raha tha
  84,16,mujhy shafaq ki qasam!aur rat ki
  84,17,Aur iski jama kerda chezon ki qasam
  84,18,Aur chand ki jab kay wo kamil hojata hay
  84,19,Yaqenan tum ik halat say dosri halat per phuncho gay
  84,20,Inhein ki hogaya kay iman nahi laty
  84,21,Aur jab in kay pass quran parha jata hay to sajda nahi kerty
  84,22,balky jinhon nay kufur kiya wo jhotla rahy hein
  84,23,aur Allah khob janta hay jo kuch yah dilon mein rakhty hein
  84,24,Inhen alamnak azabon ki khush khabri suna do
  84,25,Han eman walon aur nek amal walon be shumar aur na khtam honey wala ajar hay
  85,1,Burjoon waly asman ki qasam
  85,2,Wada kiey hoy din ki qasam
  85,3,Hazir honey waly aur hazir kiey hoy ki qasam
  85,4,(kay) kahndaqon waly halak kiey gay
  85,5,Wo ik aag thi endhan wali
  85,6,jab kay wo log uskay ass pass bethy thy
  85,7,Aur musalmano kay sath jo ker rahy thy us ko apney samney dekh rahy thy
  85,8,Yeh log in musalmano(kay kisi aur gunha ka)badla nahi lay rahy thy siway iskay wo Allah galib laeeq e hamd ki zat per iman laey thy
  85,9,jis kay liey asman o zameen ka mulk hay aur Allah Taalaa kay samney hy her chez
  85,10,Be-shak jin logon na musalman mardon aur auraton ko sataya phir tooba (bhi)na ki to unkay liey jahanum ka azab hay aur jalney ka azab hay
  85,11,Be-shak iman qabool kerney walo aur nek kam kerney walon kay liey wo baghat hein jin kay nechay nehrein beh rahi hein yehi bari kamyabi hay
  85,12,Yaqennan tery rab ki pukar bari sakht hay
  85,13,Wohi phyli martaba paida kerta hay aur wohi dobara paida kery ga
  85,14,Wo bara bakhsish kerney wala aur bohat mohabat kernay wala hay
  85,15,Arsh ka malik azmat wala hay
  85,16,jo chahy usy ker guzarney wala hay
  85,17,Tujhy lashkaron ki khabar bhi mili hay
  85,18,(Yani)firon aur samood ki
  85,19,(kuch nahi)balky kafir to jhotlaney mein pary hoy hein
  85,20,Aur Allah bhi unhein her taraf say ghery hoy hy
  85,21,Balkay yeh quran hay bari shan wala
  85,22,loh e mahfooz mein (likha hua) hay
  86,1,Qasam hay asman ki aur andhery mein roshan honay waly ki
  86,2,Tujhy maloom bhi hay ky wo raat ko namodar honey wali chez kiya hay
  86,3,Wo roshan sitara hay
  86,4,Koi asa nahi jis per nigheban farishta na ho
  86,5,Insan ko dekhna chaeiy kay kis chez say paida kiya gaya hay
  86,6,Wo ik uchalty pani say paida kiya hay
  86,7,Jo pait aur seney kay dirmiyan say nikalta hay
  86,8,Be sahk wo usy pher lyney per yaqeenan qudrat rakhney wala hay
  86,9,Jis din poshida bhedon ki janch partal hogi
  86,10,To na hoga uskay pass kuch zor na madadgar
  86,11,Barish waly asman ki qasam
  86,12,Aur pahtney wali zameen ki qasam
  86,13,Be-shak yeh (quran)albatta do tok faisla kerney wala kalam hai
  86,14,Yeh hansi ki(aur be faeeda) baat nahi
  86,15,Albatta kafir dao ghaat main nahi
  86,16,Aur mein bhi aik chaal chalraha hun
  86,17,Tu kafiron ko mohlat dey unhen thory dino chor dy
  87,1,Apney buhat hi buland Allah kay nam ki pakizgi biyan ker
  87,2,Jissney paida kiya aur sahi salim banaya
  87,3,Aur jiss na(thek thak)andaza kiya aur phir rah dekhai
  87,4,Aur jis nay taza ghass paida ki
  87,5,Phir ussney is ko (sukha ker )siyah kora ker diya
  87,6,Hum tujhy parhaein gay phir tu na bhoolay ga
  87,7,Magar jo kuch Allah chahey wo zahir aur poshida ko janta hay
  87,8,Hum apky liey asani paida kerdein gay
  87,9,To ap nasehat kerty rahein ager nasehat kuch faida dy
  87,10,Derney wala to nasehat lyga
  87,11,(han)badbakht is say gurez karey ga
  87,12,Jo bari aag mein jaey ga
  87,13,Jahan phir won a mary ga jnajeiy ga(balky halat e nazah mein para rahy ga)
  87,14,Besahk usney falah pali jo pak hogaya
  87,15,Aur jis nay apney rab ka nam yad rakha aur namaz parhta raha
  87,16,Lakin tum to duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh dyty ho
  87,17,Aur akhrat buhat bhyter aur baqa wali hay
  87,18,Yeh batein phyli kitabon mein bhi hein
  87,19,(yani) Ibrahim aur Musa ki kitabon mein
  88,1,Kiya tujhy bhi chopa lyney wali(qiyamat) ki khabar phunchi hay
  88,2,Us din bohat say chehry zalil hongy
  88,3,(aur) mehnat kerney walay thakay huye hongay
  88,4,Woh dehakti hoi aag mein jaein gy
  88,5,Aur nihayat garm chasmy ka pani unko pilaya jaey ga
  88,6,in kay liey siway-e-kanty dar darkhton kay aur kuch khana na hoga
  88,7,Jo na mota karey ga na bhook mitaey ga
  88,8,Buhat say chehry usdin tar o taza aur(asoda hall) hongy
  88,9,Apni koshish per khush hongy
  88,10,Buland o bala janaton mein hongay
  88,11,Jahan koi byhoda bat nahi sunein gaein
  88,12,Jahan bhyta hoa chashma hoga
  88,13,(Aur) us mein onchy onchy takht hongy
  88,14,Aur aabkhory rakhy hoy(hongy)
  88,15,Aur ik qatar mein lagy hoy takiey hongy
  88,16,Aur makhmali masnadein pheli pari hongi
  88,17,Kiya yeh onton ko nahi dekhty kay wok is tarah paida kiey gay hein
  88,18,Aur asmano ko kay kis tarah oncha kiya gaya hay
  88,19,Aur paharon ki tarf kay kis tarah gar dey gay hein
  88,20,Aur zameen ki tarf kay kis tarah bechaei gai hay
  88,21,Pus ap nasehat ker dia kerein (qk)ap sirf nasehat kerney waly hein
  88,22,Ap kuch in per darogha nahi hein
  88,23,Han jo shakhs rogardani kerty aur kufur kery
  88,24,usy Allah Taalaa buhat bara azab dyga
  88,25,be-shak hamari taraf inko lotna hay
  88,26,Phir be-shak hamaray zimmay hay inn say hisab lena
  89,1,Qasam hay fajar ki
  89,2,Aur das raton ki
  89,3,Aur juft aur taaq ki
  89,4,Aur raat ki jab wo chalney lagy
  89,5,Kiya inmein aqalmand kay wasty kafi qisam hay
  89,6,Kiya ap ney nahi dekha ka yap kay rab nay Qom aad kay sath kiya kiya
  89,7,Satoonon waly erum kay sath
  89,8,Jis ki manind (koi qum) mulko mein paida nahi ki gai
  89,9,Aur qum-e-samood kay sath jinho nay wadi mein bary bary pather trashy thy
  89,10,Aur firoon kay sath jo meekhon wala tha
  89,11,In sabhon nay shiron mein sir utha rakha tha
  89,12,Aur bohat fasad macha rakha tha
  89,13,Akhir tery rab nay in sab py azab ka kora barsaya
  89,14,Yaqeenan tera rab ghat mein hay
  89,15,Insan (ka yeh hal hay kay) jab ussy us ka rab azmata hay aur izat o neymat dyta hay to wo khyney lagta hay kay mery rab nay mujhy izat dar banadiya
  89,16,aur jab wo usko azmata hay aur uski rozi tang kerdyta hay to wo kehney lagta hay kay mera rab nay meri ahanat ki hy(aur zalil kiya)
  89,17,Aiaa herghiz nahi balkay (bat yeh hy) kay tum (hi)log yateemo ki izat nahi kerty
  89,18,Aur miskino kay khilaney ki ik dosry ko targheeb nahi kerty
  89,19,Aur (mardon ki)miras sameth sameth ker khaty ho
  89,20,Aur maal ko ji bhar ker aziz rakhty ho
  89,21,Yaqeenan jis waqat zameen koot koot ker baraber kerdi jaey gi
  89,22,Aur tera rab(khud )ajaey ga aur farishty safen bandh ker(ajaey gay)
  89,23,Aur jis din jhanum bhi lai jaey gi oss din insan ko samjh ayegi magar aj osky samjhney ka faida kahan
  89,24,Wo kahy ga kay kash kay mein nay apni is zindagi kay liey kuch peshgi saman kiya hota
  89,25,Pus aj Allah kay azab jaisa azab kisi ka na hoga
  89,26,Na uski qaid o band jaisi kisi ki qaid o band hogi
  89,27,Ay itmynan wali rooh
  89,28,To apney rab ki taraf loot chal is tarah kay to issy razi wo tujh say khush
  89,29,Pus mery khas bandon mein dakhil hoja
  89,30,Aur meri jannat mein chali ja
  90,1,Mein iss sher ki qasam khata hun
  90,2,aur ap is sher mein muqeem hein
  90,3,aur (qasam hy)insani bap aur olad ki
  90,4,Yaqeenan hum ney insan ko(bari)mushaqat mein paida kia hy
  90,5,kiya yeh guman kerta hy kay yeh kisis kay bas mein hi nai
  90,6,khyta (phirta )hy ky mein ney to bohat kuch maal khrch ker dala
  90,7,kiya(yun) samjhta hy ky kisi nay ussy dekha(hi ) nahi
  90,8,kiya hum nay uski do ankhein nahi banain
  90,9,aur zaban aur hunt(nahi banaey)
  90,10,hum nay dekha diy usko dono rasty
  90,11,So issy na hosakha kay ghatti mein dakhil hota
  90,12,Aur kiya samjha ky ghatti hy kiya
  90,13,Kisi garden(gulam londi)ko azad kerna
  90,14,ya bhok waly din khana khilana
  90,15,Kisi reshtydar yateem ko
  90,16,Ya khahsaar miskeen ko
  90,17,Phir unlogon mein say hojata jo iman laey aur ik dosry ko sabar ki aurreham kerney ki wasiyat kerty hein
  90,18,Yehi log hein daein bazo waly(khushbakhti waly)
  90,19,Aur jin logon nay humari aayaton kay sath kufur kiya yeh kam-bakhti waly hain
  90,20,Inn hi per aag hogi jo charo taraf say gheri hoi hogi
  91,1,Qasam hai sooraj ki aur uski dhoop ki
  91,2,Qasam hai chand ki jab uskay peechay ay
  91,3,Qasam hai din ki jab soraj ko numaya keray
  91,4,Qasam hai raat ki jab ussay dhanp lay
  91,5,Qasam hai aasman ki aur uskay bananey ki
  91,6,Qasam hai zamen ki or ussy hamwar kernay ki
  91,7,Qasam hai nafs ki or ussy durust bananey ki
  91,8,phir samjh di usko badkari ki aur bach ker chalnay ki
  91,9,Jiss nay ussay pak kiya wo kamyab hua
  91,10,Aur jiss nay ussay khak mein mila diya wo nakam hoa
  91,11,(Qom)samood nay apni sarkashi kay baees jhutlaya
  91,12,Jab unka bara badbakht uth khara hoa
  91,13,Unhein Allah kay rassol nay farmadiya tha kay Allah Taalaa ki ontni aur uss kay peeenay ki bari ki (hifazat karo)
  91,14,Un logon nay apnay pyghamber ko jhota samjh ker uss ontni ki kochein kaat dein pus unkay rab nay unkay gunahon kay baees un per halakat dali aur phir halakat ko aam kerdiya aur uss basti ko barabar ker diya
  91,15,Wo nahi darta uskay tabahkun anjam say
  92,1,Qasam hai raat ki jab cha jaey
  92,2,Aur qasam hai din ki jab roshan ho
  92,3,Aur qasam hai uss zaat ki jiss nay nar-o-mada ko peda kiya
  92,4,Yaqeenan tumhari koshish mukhtalif qisim ki hai
  92,5,Jiss nay diya (Allah ki rah mein)aur dara (apnay rab say)
  92,6,Aur nek baat ki tasdeq kerta rahega
  92,7,To hum bhi usko aasan rasty ki saholat dein gay
  92,8,Lekin jiss nay bakheel ki aur beparwai barti
  92,9,Aur nek baat ki takzeeb ki
  92,10,To hum bhi uski tangi-o-mushkil kay saman mayuser kerdein gay
  92,11,Uska maal ussy(ondha)giraney kay waqat kuch kam na ay ga
  92,12,Be-shak raah dikha dena himaray zimmay hai
  92,13,Aur humary hi hath akhrat aurduniya hai
  92,14,Mein nay to tumhein sholay marti hui aag say dara diya hai
  92,15,Jiss mein sirf wo hi badbakht dakhil hoga
  92,16,Jiss nay jhutlaya aur(uski perwi say)mun pher liya
  92,17,Aur iss say assa shaks dor rakha jaey ga jo bara perhezgar hoga
  92,18,Jo paaki hasil kernay kay liey apna maal deta hai
  92,19,Kissi ka uss per koi ehsan nahi kay jiss ka badla diya jaraha ho
  92,20,bulkay sirf apnay perwardigar buzruk-o-buland ki raza chahnay kay liey
  92,21,Yaqeenan wo (Allah bhi) un qareeb raza mand hojaeyga
  93,1,Qasam hai chasht kay waqt ki
  93,2,Aur qasam hai raat ki jab cha jaey
  93,3,Naa to tery rab nay tujhy chora hai aur na woh bezar hogaya hai
  93,4,Yaqenan tery liey injam aghaz say behter hoga
  93,5,Tujhy tere rab baht jald (inam )dyga aur to razi (o khush )hojaey ga
  93,6,Kiya us nay tujhy yateem paker jagah nahi di
  93,7,Aur tujhay raah bhola paker hidayat nahi di
  93,8,Aur tujhy na-daar paaker to-nagar nahi banadiya
  93,9,Pus yateem per to bhi sakhti na kiya ker
  93,10,Aur na sawal kernay waly ko dant dapat
  93,11,Aur apnay rab ki nematon ko biyan kerta reh
  94,1,Kiya hum nay tera seena nahi khol diya
  94,2,Aur tujh per say tera bojh hum ney utar diya
  94,3,Jiss nay teri peth tordi thi
  94,4,Aur hum nay tera zikar buland kerdiya
  94,5,Pus yaqenan mushkil kay sath asani hai
  94,6,By-shak mushkil kay sath asani hai
  94,7,Pus jab to farigh ho to ibadat mein mehnat ker
  94,8,Aur apney parwardigar hi ki tareef mein dil laga
  95,1,Qasm hai enjeer ki aur zetoon ki
  95,2,Aur toor seeneen ki
  95,3,Aur iss aman walay sher ki
  95,4,Yaqenan hum nay insan ko behtren soorat mein paida kia
  95,5,Phir isssay neechon say necha kerdiye
  95,6,lekin jo log eman laey aur (phir)nek amal kiey to inkay liey aisa ajar hai jo kabhi khatam na hoga
  95,7,Pus tujhay abb roz jaza kay jhutlanay per konsi cheez amaadah kerti hai
  95,8,Kiya Allah Taalaa (sabb) haakemon ka hakim nahi hai
  96,1,Parh apnay rab kay naam say jiss nay peda kiya
  96,2,Jiss nay insan ko khoon kay lothray say peda kiya
  96,3,tu parhta reh tera rab baray karam wala hai
  96,4,Jiss nay qalam kay zariye(ilm)sikhaya
  96,5,Jiss nay insan ko who sikhaya jissay who nai janta tha
  96,6,Such much insan to apnay say bahir hojata hy
  96,7,isliey kay who apnay apko beparwah(ya tu nagar)samjhta hy hai
  96,8,Yaqeenan lotna teray rab ki taraf hai
  96,9,(Bhala)issay bhi tumnay dekha jo bandy ko rokta hai
  96,10,Jabkay who banda salat ada kerta hai
  96,11,Bahala batla to ager who hidayat per ho
  96,12,Ya parhezgari ka hokum deta ho
  96,13,Bhala dekho to agar yeh jhutlata ho aur mun perhta ho to
  96,14,Kiya uss nay nahi jana kay Allah Taalaa ussay khob dekh raha hai
  96,15,Yaqeenan ager yeh baaz na raha to hum iski peshani kay baal paker ker ghaseetein gay
  96,16,Aisi peshani jo jhooti katakar hai
  96,17,yeh apni majlis walon ko bulalay
  96,18,hum bhi (dozakh kay)piyadon ko bula lein gy
  96,19,Khabardar! isska kehna hergiz na manna aur sajda ker aur qareeb hoja
  97,1,Yaqeenan hum nay issay shab qadar mein nazil farmaya
  97,2,To kiaya janey kay shab qadar kiya hy
  97,3,Shab qadar aik hazar maheeno say behter hai
  97,4,Iss (mein her kaam) kay siranjam denay ko apney rab kay hukum say farishty aur rooh(jibrael)utertay hain
  97,5,Yeh raat sir-a-sir slamti ki hoti hai aur fajar kay tuloo honay tak(rehti hai)
  98,1,Ehl-e-kitab kay kafir aur mushrik log jabb tak kay unkay pass zahir daleel na ajaye baz rehnay waly na thay(who daleel yeh thi kay)
  98,2,Allah Taalaa ka aik rasol jo pak saheefay parhay
  98,3,jin mein sahi aur durust ehkam hon
  98,4,Ehl-e-kitab apnay pass zahir daleel ajanay kay baad hi (ikhtilaaf mein par ker) mutafarriq hogaey
  98,5,Unhein isskay siwa koi hokum nahi diya gaya kay sirf Allah ki ibadat kerein ussi kay liey deen ko khalis rakhein.ibraheem hanif kay deen per aur salat ko qaem rakhein aur zakat dety rahen yehi hai deen sedhi millat ka
  98,6,Be-shak jo log ehl-e-kitab mein say kafir huye aur mushrikeen sab dozakh ki aag mein(jaeigy)jahan who hamesha(hamesha)reheingy.yeh log bad tareen khalaeeq hain
  98,7,Be-shak jo log eman laey aur nek amal kiey yeh log behtreen khalaeeq hain
  98,8,Inn ka badla unkay rab kay pass hameshgi wohi jannaten hein jinkay neechy nehrein beh rahi hein jin mein who hamesha hamesha rahein gay.Allah Taalaa unsy razi hua aur yeh uss say razi huye.yeh hai uskay liey jo apnay perwardigar say daray
  99,1,Jabb zameen pori tarah jhanjor di jaeygi
  99,2,Aur apney bojh bahar nikal phenkay gi
  99,3,Insan kehnay lagay ga kay issay kiya hogaya
  99,4,Uss din zameen apni sabb khabrein biyan kerdegi
  99,5,Issliye kay tery rab nay ussy hukam diya hoga
  99,6,Uss rozlog mukhtalif jamatein hoker(wapis)lotein gay takey unhein unkay aiymaal dikha diey jaein
  99,7,pus jiss nay zara baraber neki ki hogi who issay dekhlega
  99,8,Aur jiss nay zara baraber burai ki hogi who ussy dekhlega
  100,1,Hanpety hoye dorney waly ghoron ki qasam
  100,2,Phir taap maar ker aag jharnay walon ki qasam
  100,3,Phir subha kay waqat dhawa bolney walon ki qasam
  100,4,Pus uss waqat gard-o-ghubar uraty hein
  100,5,Phir ussi kay sath fojon kay darmiyan ghos jaty hein
  100,6,Yaqeenan insan apnay rab ka bara nashukra hy
  100,7,Aur yaqeenan who khud bhi issi per gawah hai
  100,8,Yeh maal ki muhabbat mein bhi bara sakht hai
  100,9,Kiya issay who waqat maloom nahi jabb qabron mein jo kuch hy nikal liya jaey ga
  100,10,Aur seenon ki poshida batein zahir kerdi jaeingi
  100,11,Be-shak inka rab uss din unkay haal say poora ba-khabar hoga
  101,1,Kharkhara deney wali
  101,2,Kiaya hy who kharkhara deney wali
  101,3,Tujhay kiya maloom kay who kharkhara deney wali kia hy
  101,4,Jiss din insan bikhray huye perwanon ki tarah hojaeyen gy
  101,5,Aur pahar dhunay huye rangeen oon ki tarah hojaein gay
  101,6,phir jiss kay palry bhari hongy
  101,7,Who to dilpasand aram ki zindagi mein hoga
  101,8,Aur jiss kay palry halky hongy
  101,9,uss ka thikana Laaviya hai
  101,10,Tujhy kia maloom kay yeh kiya hai
  101,11,woh Tand-o-tez aag (hai)
  102,1,Zeyadti ki chahat nay tumhein ghafil kerdia
  102,2,Yahan tak kay tum qabastan ja phunchy
  102,3,Hergiz nahi tum unqareeb maloom kerlogay
  102,4,Hergiz nahi phir tumhein jald ilm hojaey ga
  102,5,Hergiz nahi ager tum yaqeeni tor per jan lo
  102,6,To be-shak tum jahanum dekhlogay
  102,7,Aur tum ussy yaqeen ki aankh say dekhlogy
  102,8,Phir uss din tum say zarror bil-zaroor nematon ka sawal hoga
  103,1,Zamaney ki qasam
  103,2,Beyshak (bil-yaqeen)insane sir ta sir nuqsan mein hay
  103,3,Siwaey un logon kay jo eman laey aur nek amal kiey aur(jinhon nay)apas mein haq ki waseeyat ki aur aik doosry ko sabar ki naseehat ki
  104,1,Bari kharabi hai her aisy shaks ki jo aib tatolney wala geebat kerney wala ho
  104,2,Jo maal ko jama kerta jaey or ginta jaey
  104,3,Woh samjhta hy kay uska maal usky pass sada rahay ga
  104,4,Hergiz nahi yeh to zaroor tor phor denay wali aag mein phenk diya jaeyga
  104,5,Aur tujhey kia maloom kay asi aag kiya hogi
  104,6,Woh Allah Taalaa ki sulgai hoi aag hogi
  104,7,Jo dilon per charhti chali jaey gi
  104,8,Who unn per her taraf say band ki hui hogi
  104,9,Bary bary satoonon mein
  105,1,Kia tu nay na dekha kay tery rab nay hathi walon kay sath kia kiya
  105,2,Kia unkay maker ko beykar nai kerdia
  105,3,Aur unper parindon kay jhond kay jhond bhej diey
  105,4,Jo unhein mitti or pather ki kankariyan mar rahy thy
  105,5,Pus unhein khaye huye bhoosy ki tarah kerdiya
  106,1,Quresh kay manoos kerney kay liye
  106,2,(yanni) unhen jary aur garmi kay safar say manoos kerney kay liey.(uskay shukriey main)
  106,3,Pus unhen chahey kay issi gher kay rab ki ibadat kerty rahen
  106,4,Jiss nay inhen bhook mein khana diya aur darr (aur khof) mein aman (o-aman) diya
  107,1,Kiya tu nay(ussay bhi)dekha jo (roz) jaza ko jhutlata hai
  107,2,yehi who hai jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai
  107,3,Aur miskeen ko khilaney ki targeeb nahi deta
  107,4,Un namazion kay liey afsos(aur well nami jahanum ki jagah)hai
  107,5,Jo apni namaz say ghafil hain
  107,6,Jo riya kari kerty hein
  107,7,Aur baratnay ki chez roktay hain
  108,1,Yaqeenan hum nay tujhay (hoz)kusar (aur bhat kuch) diya hay
  108,2,Pus tu apney rab kay liey namz parh aur qurbani karo
  108,3,Yaqeenan tera dushman hi la-waris aur benam-o-nishan hai
  109,1,Aap khydijey kay aey kafiro
  109,2,Na mein ibadat kerta hun usski jiss kit um ibadat kerty ho
  109,3,Na tum ibadat kerney waly ho usski jisski mein ibadat kerta hon
  109,4,Aur na mein ibadat karon ga uski jisski tum ibadat kerty ho
  109,5,Aur na tum usski ibadat kerney waly hojisski mein ibadat ker raha hon
  109,6,Tumhary liey tumhara deen hai aur mery liey mera deen hai
  110,1,Jab Allah ji madad aur fatah ajaye
  110,2,Aur tu logon ko ALLAH kay deen mein jok dar jok aata dekh lay
  110,3,To apnay rabb ki tasbeeh karney lag hamd kay sath aur uss say maghfirat ki dua maang bey shak woh bara hi tauba qabool karney wala hai
  111,1,Abu Lahab ky dono hath toot gaye aur who (khud) halk ho gaya
  111,2,Na to uska maal usky kaam aya aur na uski kamai
  111,3,Who unqareeb bharkney waali aag mein jaey ga
  111,4,Aur uski biwi bhi(jaeygi)jo lakriyan dhonay waali hai
  111,5,usski gardan mein post khajoor ki bati hui rassi hogi
  112,1,Aap kehydijiye kay Woh ALLAH TaALA aik(hi)hai
  112,2,Allah bey niaz hai
  112,3,Na uss say koi paida hoa na who kisi say paida hoa
  112,4,Aur na koi uska humser hai
  113,1,Aap kehdijiye! Kay mein subha ky Rab ki panah mein aata hun
  113,2,Her uss cheez ky shar say jo uss nay paida ki hai
  113,3,Aur andheri raat ki tareki kay shar say jab uska andhera phel jaye
  113,4,Aur girah(laga ker inn)mein phonknay walon kay sher say(bhi)
  113,5,Aur hasad kerney waly ki burai say bhi jab wo hasad karey
  114,1,Aap kehdijiey!kay mein logo kay parwardigar ki panah mein ata hun
  114,2,Logon ky malik ki(aur)
  114,3,Logon ky maabood ki(Panah mein)
  114,4,Waswasa dalney waly pechy hut janey waly kay shar say
  114,5,Jo logon kay seenon mein waswasa daalta hai
  114,6,(Khua) woh jinn mein say ho ya insaan mein say